%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIvanov%2C%20who%20led%20evacuations%20out%20of%20Soledar%20throughout%20the%20summer%20and%20fall%2C%20recalled%20the%20two%20months%20after%20the%20fighting%20began%20as%20particularly%20volatile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225368%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ivanov%20and%20Synia%20helped%20evacuate%20people%20from%20Soledar%20throughout%20the%20summer%20and%20fall.%20Most%20people%20who%20needed%20help%20were%20older%20adults%2C%20they%20said.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650b6da0bf943d00195c981a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224026%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIvanov%20and%20Synia%20helped%20evacuate%20people%20from%20Soledar%20throughout%20the%20summer%20and%20fall.%20Most%20people%20who%20needed%20help%20were%20older%20adults%2C%20they%20said.%3Cp%3ETania%20Synia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20so%20fast%20and%20it%20was%20so%20hot%2C%26quot%3B%20Ivanov%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20so%20many%20people%20in%20August%20decided%20to%20go%20from%20Soledar%2C%20because%20it%20was%20sometimes%20really%20dangerous.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20August%2C%20Ivanov%20estimated%20he%20evacuated%20as%20many%20as%2060%20people%20a%20day%20out%20of%20Soledar.%20Synia%20joined%20Ivanov%20for%20one%20such%20evacuation%20trip%20on%20August%2014%2C%202022.%20Synia%20arrived%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%20after%20Ukrainian%20officials%20confirmed%20Soledar%20was%20under%20attack%2C%20and%20she%20estimated%20the%20city%20was%20already%20about%2090%25%20destroyed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20smell%20the%20bombing%20and%20the%20smoke%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shelling%20was%20constant%2C%20Synia%20said%2C%20with%20shots%20ringing%20out%20about%20every%2010%20minutes.%20Volunteers%20had%20little%20time%20to%20convince%20residents%20to%20evacuate%20before%20they%20themselves%20had%20to%20flee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3