ia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20time%20in%20Soledar%2C%20Cherniavska%20was%20stationed%20near%20the%20fallen%20town%20at%20a%20stabilization%20point%20that%20saw%20about%20200%20casualties%20a%20day%20through%20January%20and%20February.%20She%20said%20most%20of%20those%20men%20came%20from%20Soledar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20left%20at%20least%20a%20part%20of%20me%20in%20Soledar%2C%26quot%3B%20Cherniavska%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20anguish%20was%20nothing%20compared%20to%20what%20she%20witnessed%20among%20the%20soldiers%20who%20arrived%20from%20a%20fallen%20Soledar%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20psychologically%20wounded%2C%26quot%3B%20Cherniavska%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20would%20scream.%20They%20would%20cry.%20They%20would%20behave%20irrationally.%20They%20would%20drag%20their%20guns.%20Again%20and%20again.%20They%20would%20tremble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-wagner-group-decimated-soledar-for-short-lived-political-win-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699788181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e951bb788914e5554514f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-wagner-group-decimated-soledar-for-short-lived-political-win-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Leading%20up%20to%20Soledar's%20fall%2C%20Russia%20believed%20seizing%20the%20town%20would%20lead%20to%20victory%20in%20Bakhmut.%20Witnesses%20described%20the%20town's%20gradual%20disappearance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnodgrass%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Snodgrass)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-wagner-group-decimated-soledar-for-short-lived-political-win-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20Bigger%20Countries...%26quot%3B%3A%20Trudeau's%20Fresh%20Barb%20At%20India%20Amid%20Diplomatic%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20fresh%20remarks%20on%20the%20diplomatic%20face-off%20with%20India%2C%20Canada's%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20has%20said%20that%20the%20world%20will%20become%20%26quot%3Bmore%20dangerous%26quot%3B%20for%20everyone%20%26quot%3Bif%20bigger%20countries%20can%20violate%20international%20law%20without%20consequences%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Ottawa%20have%20been%20strained%20ever%20since%20Trudeau%20accused%20Indian%20agents%20of%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20Nijjar%2C%2045%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20outside%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20Canada's%20British%20Columbia%20in%20June.%20He%20was%20chief%20of%20the%20banned%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20and%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20wanted%20terrorists.%20India%20has%20termed%20the%20allegations%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20addressing%20the%20media%20at%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20countrywide%20smart%20energy%20grid.%20Responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20US%20should%20take%20up%20the%20matter%20with%20India%20on%20Canada's%20behalf%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20when%20we%20learnt%20of%20credible%20allegations%20that%20agents%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizens%20on%20Canadian%20soil%2C%20we%20reached%20out%20to%20India%20to%20ask%20them%20to%20work%20with%20us%20in%20getting%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%20matter.%20We%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20our%20friends%20and%20allies%2C%20like%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20others%20to%20work%20on%20these%20really%20serious%20violation%20of%20international%20law%20and%20sovereignty%20of%20a%20democracy.%20This%20is%20something%20we%20are%20taking%20very%20very%20seriously%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20with%20all%20partners%20as%20law%20enforcement%20and%20investigative%20agencies%20continue%20to%20do%20their%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCanada%20is%20a%20country%20that%20will%20always%20stand%20up%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20because%20if%20might%20starts%20to%20make%20right%2C%20if%20bigger%20countries%20can%20violate%20international%20law%20without%20consequences%2C%20then%20the%20whole%20world%20gets%20more%20dangerous%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20Canadian%20MP%20Chandra%20Arya's%20invitation%20to%20Indian%20envoy%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Verma%20for%20an%20event%20was%20appropriate%20amid%20the%20diplomatic%20face-off%2C%20Trudeau%20said%20Canada%20wants%20to%20%26quot%3Bwork%20constructively%26quot%3B%20with%20India%20on%20this%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%20matter%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20to%20partners%20around%20the%20world%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%2C%20to%20take%20it%20seriously.%20That's%20why%20we%20were%20so%20disappointed%20when%20India%20violated%20the%20Vienna%20convention%20and%20arbitratrily%20revoked%20the%20diplomatic%20immunity%20of%20over%2040%20Canadian%20diplomats%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20serious%20reasons%20to%20believe%20that%20agents%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%20could%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20on%20Canadian%20soil.%20And%20India's%20response%20is%20to%20kick%20out%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20Canadian%20diplomats%20by%20violating%20their%20rights%20under%20the%20Vienna%20convention.%20That%20is%20of%20concern%20to%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20because%20if%20a%20given%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Canada%20Prime%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20said%20Canada%20has%20tried%20to%20%26quot%3Bwork%20constructively%26quot%3B%20with%20India%20and%20that%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20fight%20we%20want%20to%20be%20having%20right%20now%20but%20we%20will%20always%20unequivocally%20stand%20up%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20is%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20Trudeau's%20latest%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20firm%20response%20to%20Trudeau's%20allegations%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20said%20that%20they%20have%20told%20Ottawa%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20not%20the%20government%20of%20India's%20policy%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20told%20them%20that%20look%2C%20if%20you%20have%20something%20specific%2C%20if%20you%20have%20something%20relevant%2C%20let%20us%20know.%20We%20are%20open%20to%20looking%20at%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20Canada%20actually%20has%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20organised%20crime%20relating%20to%20the%20secessionist%20forces%2C%20organised%20crime%2C%20violence%2C%20extremism.%20They're%20all%20very%2C%20very%20deeply%20mixed%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jaishankar%20also%20raised%20concern%20over%20Indian%20diplomats%20and%20consulates%20facing%20threats%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20situation%20where%20actually%20our%20diplomats%20are%20threatened%2C%20our%20consulates%20have%20been%20attacked%20and%20often%20comments%20are%20made%20about%20'there's%20interference%20in%20our%20politics'.%20And%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20this%20is%20often%20justified%20as%20saying%2C%20well%2C%20that's%20how%20democracies%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699788180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fmhrljs64_justin-trudeau-modi_625x300_23_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2