tition%2C%20an%20expensive%20manufacturing%20process%2C%20and%20shareholders%20who%20have%20grown%20used%20to%20fat%20profits.%20If%20cutting%20prices%20is%20all%20Tesla%20can%20do%20to%20survive%20this%20new%20reality%2C%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20bleed%20money%20every%20time%20the%20rubber%20hits%20the%20road.%20And%20at%20some%20point%2C%20turning%20it%20around%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Flinette-lopez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELinette%20Lopez%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-price-cuts-electric-cars-losing-business-strategy-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699788121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654d33163cc84b4dfaffa648%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-price-cuts-electric-cars-losing-business-strategy-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20has%20spent%20the%20past%20year%20slashing%20its%20prices%20to%20try%20and%20drive%20away%20the%20competition.%20That's%20a%20losing%20strategy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22llopez%40insider.com%20(Linette%20Lopez)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-price-cuts-electric-cars-losing-business-strategy-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WeWork%20was%20doomed%20to%20fail%20by%20taking%20on%20huge%20buildings%2C%20rival%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22WeWork%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654b88993cc84b4dfafe6742%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWeWork's%20huge%20coworking%20spaces%20are%20a%20common%20sight%20in%20many%20city%20centers.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWeWork%20was%20famous%20for%20huge%20coworking%20spaces%20with%20amenities%20like%20climbing%20walls%20and%20swimming%20pools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIndustrious%20CEO%20Jamie%20Hodari%20said%20they%20saddled%20the%20company%20with%20big%20liabilities%20and%20weren't%20viable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWeWork%2C%20once%20valued%20at%20%2447%20billion%2C%20has%20declared%20bankruptcy%20after%20years%20of%20financial%20difficulties.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWeWork's%20collapse%20has%20ended%20the%20era%20of%20enormous%20coworking%20spaces%20filled%20with%20amenities%20like%20climbing%20walls%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.architecturaldigest.com%2Fstory%2Ffirst-look-inside-weworks-largest-office-space%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elive%20DJs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wework.com%2Fen-GB%2Fideas%2Fworkspace-solutions%2Fflexible-products%2Foffice-amenities%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eswimming%20pools%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20boss%20of%20one%20of%20its%20main%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustrious%20CEO%20Jamie%20Hodari%20told%20Insider%20that%20while%20many%20WeWork%20locations%20will%20simply%20change%20hands%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwework-files-for-bankruptcy-chapter-11-commercial-real-estate-reckoning-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efollowing%20the%20company's%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20huge%20office%20blocks%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wework.com%2Fen-GB%2Fideas%2Fworkspace-solutions%2Foffice-amenities%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluxurious%20amenities%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20become%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20cost%20of%