orward%2C%20and%20the%20sheer%20scale%20of%20their%20liabilities%20overall%2C%20are%20a%20symptom%20of%20a%20go-go%20era%20where%20people%20were%20running%20companies%20for%20revenue%20growth%20rather%20than%20with%20an%20eye%20to%20profitability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLots%20of%20companies%2C%20WeWork%20included%2C%20made%20decisions%20that%20spiked%20revenue%20in%20the%20short%20run%2C%20but%20probably%20weren't%20prudent%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELuxurious%20coworking%20spaces%20may%20be%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHuge%20coworking%20spaces%20filled%20with%20yoga%20rooms%2C%20beer%20taps%2C%20and%20swimming%20pools%20were%20the%20hallmark%20of%20WeWork's%20operation%20at%20its%20height.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBriggs%20Elwell%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20real%20estate%20finance%20company%20RLTY%20Capital%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20as%20impressive%20as%20these%20locations%20were%2C%20they%20were%20not%20helpful%20for%20the%20company%20as%20it%20attempted%20to%20become%20profitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20looked%20at%20the%20financials%20of%20WeWork%20even%20before%20this%20downfall%2C%20back%20in%20the%20days%20of%20%5BAdam%5D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwework-co-founder-adam-neumann-is-stepping-down-as-ceo-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENeumann%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20it%20was%20pretty%20clear%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20luxuries%20were%20actually%20the%20differentiating%20factor%20between%20profitability%20and%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwework-cofounder-adam-neumann-on-its-collapse-bankruptcy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENeumann%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20a%20cofounder%20and%20former%20CEO%20of%20WeWork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20regrettably%20that%20you're%20probably%20not%20going%20to%20have%20