%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-are-my-student-loans-in-forbearance-mohela-borrowers-repayment-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplace%20all%20impacted%20borrowers%20on%20administrative%20forbearance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmy%20experienced%20one%20of%20those%20errors%20firsthand.%20With%20just%20under%20%2430%2C000%20in%20student%20debt%20from%20her%20undergraduate%20education%2C%20Amy%20%E2%80%94%20who%20requested%20to%20use%20a%20pseudonym%20to%20protect%20her%20privacy%20but%20whose%20full%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20Insider%20%E2%80%94%20decided%20to%20pursue%20a%20teaching%20certificate%20through%20online%20courses%20partly%20funded%20by%20a%20private%20scholarship%20for%20veterans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%20account%2C%20reviewed%20by%20Insider%2C%20payments%20on%20her%20undergraduate%20loans%20were%20in%20an%20in-school%20deferment%20status%2C%20meaning%20she%20would%20not%20be%20required%20to%20enter%20repayment%20on%20those%20loans%20until%20she%20earned%20her%20certificate%20in%20December%202024.%20However%2C%20prior%20to%20beginning%20her%20teaching%20program%2C%20Amy's%20loans%20were%20in%20auto-debit%20to%20earn%20a%200.25%20percentage%20point%20reduction%20on%20interest%20rates%2C%20and%20MOHELA%20did%20not%20cease%20auto-debit%20despite%20her%20deferment%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Amy%20was%20able%20to%20successfully%20dispute%20the%20charge%20with%20her%20bank%2C%20she's%20worried%20the%20issue%20might%20happen%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20excuse%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Amy%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she's%20concerned%20she'll%20have%20to%20take%20MOHELA%20to%20small%20claims%20court%20someday.%20%26quot%3BBut%20nobody%20has%20the%20time%20to%20take%20a%20stand%20against%20it%2C%20and%20I%20wonder%20how%20many%20other%20borrowers%20are%20having%20money%20taken%20out%20their%20account%20wrongly%2C%20that%20are%20being%20charged%20interest%20wrongly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp