f%20FSA%20does%20not%20fully%20remediate%20these%20borrowers%2C%20they%20will%20likely%20find%20violations%20of%20their%20consumer%20protection%20laws%20and%20require%20servicers%20to%20remediate%20the%20problems%20experienced%20by%20borrowers%20themselves%20and%20impose%20monetary%20fines%20against%20the%20servicers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmy%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrower-paid-off-remaining-balance-debt-payment-due-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20student-loan%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20previously%20told%20Insider%20they%20mulled%20legal%20action%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20challenges%20with%20repayment%20that%20had%20yet%20to%20be%20resolved.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20ridiculous%20these%20companies%20get%20contracts%20for%20federal%20student%20loans%2C%26quot%3B%20Amy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20department%20has%20promised%20continued%20oversight%20over%20servicers.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-bad-customer-service-education-department-oversight-repayment-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereleased%20new%20guidance%20on%20enforcing%20accountability%20over%20servicers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stating%20that%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20will%20monitor%20customer%20service%20calls%20and%20partner%20with%20state%20and%20federal%20regulators%20to%20enforce%20consumer%20protection%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20also%20said%20it%20might%20transfer%20borrowers%20to%20other%20servicers%20if%20a%20servicer%20shows%20it's%20%26quot%3Bunable%20to%20perform%20their%20duties%20for%20the%20borrowers%20they%20manage%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20would%20stunt%20compensation%20for%20the%20targeted%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Biden-Harris%20Administration%20has%20made%20clear%20that%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20borrowers%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20unacceptable%2