aine%20intelligence%20services%20and%20took%20orders%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-iron-general-west-mine-clearing-equipment-insufficient-russia-war-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20country's%20top%20general%2C%20Valery%20Zaluzhny%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20paper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20has%20long%20denied%20his%20country's%20involvement%20in%20the%20attacks%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20massive%20gas%20leaks%20and%20strained%20diplomatic%20relations%20between%20Ukraine%20and%20Western%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20The%20Post%20reported%20that%20Zelenskyy%20would%20not%20have%20known%20about%20the%20Nord%20Stream%20operation%20and%20that%20those%20involved%20reported%20to%20Zaluzhny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20conclusion%20is%20based%20on%20intelligence%20reporting%20obtained%20by%20the%20CIA%20through%20accused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjack-teixeira-stockpiling-weapons-before-arrest-classified-leaks-nyt-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPentagon%20leaker%20Jack%20Teixeira.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChervinsky%20denied%20his%20role%20in%20the%20attacks%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20papers%20through%20his%20lawyer%3A%20%26quot%3BAll%20speculations%20about%20my%20involvement%20in%20the%20attack%20on%20Nord%20Stream%20are%20being%20spread%20by%20Russian%20propaganda%20without%20any%20basis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChervinsky%20is%20currently%20being%20held%20in%20jail%20in%20Kyiv%20over%20a%20scheme%20to%20lure%20a%20Russian%20pilot%20to%20defect%20to%20Ukraine%20last%20year%2C%20during%20which%20he%20is%20accused%20of%20inadvertently%20revealing%20a%20Ukrainian%20airfield's%20coordinates%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20Russian%20rocket%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20blasts%20in%20September%20last%20year%20damaged%20three%20of%20the%20four%20pipelines%20that%20make%20up%20Nord%20Stream%201%20and%20Nord%20Stream%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20had%20long%20complained%20that%20the%20pipelines%20would%20enable%20Russia%20to%20circumvent%20Ukrainian%20pipes%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20transit%20revenue%20for%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pipelines%20were%20not%20operational%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20attack%20due%20to%20disputes%20between%20Russia%20and%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-military-key-role-sabotaging-the-nord-stream-pipelines2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699786818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6550a613385143459e8bbdbe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-military-key-role-sabotaging-the-nord-stream-pipelines2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20investigation%20links%20a%20senior%20Ukrainian%20military%20official%20to%20Nord%20Stream%20pipeline%20sabotage%20for%20the%20first%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ashoaib%40insider.com%20(Alia%20Shoaib)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-military-key-role-sabotaging-the-nord-stream-pipelines2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Photos%3A%20How%20Goa%20Celebrates%20Diwali%20With%20the%20Symbolic%20Slaying%20of%20Narakasura%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F12155945%2FNarkasur-15.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EPanjim%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20festival%20of%20lights%2C%20which%20is%20celebrated%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20ways%20across%20India%2C%20takes%20on%20a%20unique%20charm%20in%20the%20coastal%20region%20of%20Goa%20with%20Narkasur%20Chaturdashi.%20On%20the%20eve%20of%20Diwali%2C%20hundreds%20of%20community-made%20and%20home-made%20effigies%20of%20Narakasura%20are%20paraded%20on%20the%20streets%20before%20being%20burnt%20in%20a%20symbolic%20slaying%20of%20the%20demon%20king.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Hindu%20mythology%2C%20Narakasura%20was%20a%20powerful%20king%20who%20had%20gained%20invincibility%20through%20a%20boon.%20However%2C%20his%20arrogance%20and%20misuse%20of%20power%20led%20to%20tyranny.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20pleas%20of%20his%20subjects%2C%20Krishna%20confronted%20Narakasura.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20fierce%20battle%2C%20Krishna%20ultimately%20vanquished%20the%20demon%2C%20liberating%20over%20a%20thousand%20captive%20women%20and%20restoring%20justice%20and%20honour.%20The%20victory%20of%20Krishna%20over%20Narakasura%20is%20celebrated%20during%20Diwali%2C%20symbolising%20the%20triumph%20of%20righteousness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20each%20passing%20year%2C%20localities%20have%20been%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20competitive.%20In%20villages%20and%20towns%20across%20Goa%2C%20groups%20of%20young%20men%20%E2%80%93%20proudly%20labelled%20%E2%80%98the%20Pirate%20Boys%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Sanskaari%20boys%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Anjuna%20boyz%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20like%20%E2%80%93%20pull%20in%20funding%2C%20come%20up%20with%20a%20creative%20concept%20and%20get%20moving%20on%20getting%20materials%20together%20for%20the%20all-night%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20one%20demon%20king%20with%20dreadlocks%2C%20to%20many%20more%20with%20sinewy%20muscular%20thighs%20to%20yet%20more%20with%20snake-like%20lower%20bodies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20interpretations%20are%20many.%20The%20effigies%20are%20decorated%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20ways%2C%20from%20golden%20chains%2C%20to%20whips%20made%20of%20neon%20light%20and%20even%20accomplices%20like%20the%20evil%20spirit%20from%20Hollywood%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Nun%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%