cludes%20noting%20stuff%20you%20recommend%20on%20your%20Amazon%20page.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20side%20hustles%20he%20was%20surprised%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BContent%20creation%20can%20range%20from%20a%20part-time%20passion%20to%20a%20full-time%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20several%20ways%20creators%20can%20earn%2C%20including%20linking%20to%20qualifying%20products%2C%20promoting%20Amazon%20services%20like%20Prime%20video%20and%20Amazon%20Music%2C%20curating%20shoppable%20photo%20and%20video%20content%20and%20livestreaming%20and%20recommending%20products%20through%20Amazon%20Live%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20said%20he%20did%20a%20video%20of%20a%20product%20and%20that%20it%20got%20on%20the%20product's%20page.%20He%20said%20he%20got%20commission%20from%20that%2C%20noting%20he%20made%20some%20earnings%20%26quot%3Bjust%20from%20uploading%20these%20videos%20that%20passively%20get%20watched%20while%20during%20the%20purchase%20journey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20made%20%2416.45%20from%20his%20influencer%20page%2C%20which%20he%20wants%20to%20double%20down%20on%20and%20try%20out%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20interested%20in%20this%20program%20should%20know%20that%20they%20have%20to%20have%20one%20of%20the%20following%2C%20per%20an%20Amazon%20spokesperson%3A%20a%20YouTube%2C%20Instagram%2C%20TikTok%2C%20or%20Facebook%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20sign%20up%2C%20we%20will%20review%20your%20submission%20details%20and%20determine%20whether%20you%20qualify%20for%20the%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20look%20at%20many%20factors%20when%20assessing%20applicants%2C%20including%20content%2C%20engagement%20rate%20and%20following%20size.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUser-generated%20content%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20previously%20told%20Insider%20about%20his%20success%20making%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-money-from-ugc-user-generated-content-ads%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Euser-generated%20content%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20UGC%2C%20using%20a%20platform%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjoinbrands.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoinBrands%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20this%20is%20still%20a%20pursuit%20he%20would%20recommend%20given%20it's%20%26quot%3Ba%20pretty%20low%20lift%20side%20hustle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20recommend%20user-generated%20content%20as%20a%20side%20hustle%20because%20it%20offers%20a%20win-win%20scenario%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20not%20only%20receive%20products%20for%20free%20but%20also%20get%20paid%20for%20relatively%20straightforward%20tasks.%20This%20side%20hustle%20is%20ideal%20for%20individuals%20who%20are%20comfortable%20in%20front%20of%20a%20camera%20or%20possess%20some%20creative%20photography%20skills.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20%2478%20for%20one%20product%20review%20he%20did%2C%20and%20he%20kept%20the%20product%20after.%20He%20earned%20%2415%20for%20UGC%20of%20a%20tree%20stand%20and%20earned%20%2460%20for%20making%20a%20video%20about%20a%20bike%20lock.%20Documentation%20shared%20with%20Insider%20shows%20Ryan%20has%20nearly%20%241%2C500%20in%20total%20earnings%20on%20JoinBrands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20allow%20creators%20to%20take%20jobs%20with%20brands%20instantly%2C%26quot%3B%20Ian%20Sells%2C%20cofounder%20of%20JoinBrands%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20marketplace%20full%20of%20basically%20jobs%20which%20are%20posted%20by%20brands%2C%20and%20then%20the%20creators%20can%20select%20or%20apply%20to%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESells%20said%20once%20the%20creator%20is%20chosen%2C%20they%20can%20get%20the%20product%20and%20then%20will%20make%20the%20content%20before%20getting%20paid%20on%20the%20JoinBrands%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20great%20thing%20ab