3BSelling%20Sunset%2C%26quot%3B%20there's%20yet%20more%20drama%20over%20pricey%20houses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20time%2C%20it%20hinges%20on%20Los%20Angeles'%20new%20mansion%20tax%2C%20which%20impacts%20homes%20sold%20for%20over%20%245%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tax%20is%20designed%20to%20fund%20affordable%20housing%2C%20but%20it%20may%20be%20flawed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%2010%20minutes%20into%20the%20new%20season%20of%20the%20hit%20Netflix%20reality%20show%20%26quot%3BSelling%20Sunset%2C%26quot%3B%20two%20luxury%20real%20estate%20brokers%20are%20already%20complaining%20about%20a%20new%20tax%20on%20Los%20Angeles'%20wealthiest%20homebuyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20nightmare%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20veteran%20real%20estate%20agent%20Mary%20Fitzgerald.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20just%20screwed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city's%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bmansion%20tax%26quot%3B%20was%20about%20to%20go%20into%20effect%20when%20the%20show%20was%20filming%20its%20latest%20season%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20the%20high-end%20real%20estate%20industry%20was%20in%20a%20tizzy.%20The%20owner%20of%20one%20%2426%20million%2C%2013%2C000-square-foot%20home%20the%20agents%20were%20trying%20to%20sell%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20an%20extra%20%241.43%20million%20in%20taxes%20under%20the%20new%20law.%20The%20policy%2C%20which%20went%20into%20effect%20on%20April%201%2C%202023%2C%20levies%20an%20extra%204%25%20tax%20on%20homes%20sold%20for%20more%20than%20%245%20million%20and%20a%205.5%25%20tax%20on%20those%20over%20%2410%20million.%20The%20'%26quot%3BSelling%20Sunset%26quot%3B%20agents%20were%20terrified%20their%20business%20would%20dry%20up%20with%20owners%20scared%20off%20by%20the%20new%20tax%2C%20on%20top%20of%20high%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20are%20huge%20numbers%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20massive%20detriment%20to%20the%20real%20estate%20market%20as%20a%20whole%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20agents%2C%20Nicole%20Young%2C%20tells%20the%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agents'%20boss%20at%20the%20Oppenheim%20Group%20brokerage%2C%20Jason%20Oppenheim%2C%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.curbed.com%2F2023%2F03%2Fmansion-tax-los-angeles-april-1.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%20clients%20in%20an%20email%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20new%20tax%20%26quot%3Bdefies%20common%20sense%20and%20basic%20logic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20often%20that%20a%20tax%20measure%20becomes%20a%20vehicle%20for%20reality%20show%20drama.%20But%20the%20omnipresence%20of%20LA's%20mansion%20tax%20is%20felt%20throughout%20the%20seventh%20season%20of%20the%20soapy%20real%20estate%20reality%20drama%2C%20as%20agents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-mansion-tax-causing-big-homes-heavily-discounted-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Escramble%20to%20sell%20ahead%20of%20its%20implementation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20have%20tough%20conversations%20with%20their%20clients.%20And%20the%20Oppenheim%20brokers%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0best%20known%20for%20marketing%20obscenely%20flashy%20homes%20while%20making%20similarly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F11%2F03%2Frealestate%2Fselling-sunset-netflix-season-7-fashion.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eshowy%20sartorial%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20choices%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0aren't%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELA's%20new%20tax%20was%20designed%20to%20raise%20dedicated%20revenue%20for%20affordable%20housing%20and%20homelessness%20prevention%2C%20but%20some%20advocates%20might%20agree%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BSelling%20Sunset%26quot%3B%20agents%20that%20the%20law%20is%20flawed%20%E2%80%94%20just%20not%20for%20all%20the%20same%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20high-end%20realtors%20worry%20about%20their%20sales%2C%20some%20housing%20advocates%20are%20celebrating%20the%20new%20tax.%20Just%2016%25%20of%20Californians%20can%20afford%20to%20purchase%20a%20single-family%20home%20at%20the%20state-wide%20median%20price%20of%20more%20than%20%24840%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20a%20housing%20affordability%20report%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.car.org%2Fen%2Fmarketdata%2Fdata%2Fhaitraditional%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECalifornia%20Association%20of%20Realtors%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20you'd%20need%20a%20minimum%20income%20of%20%24198%2C000%20for%20that%20to%20be%20feasible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F73vx6%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Housing%20affordability%20index%20for%20LA%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20affordable%20housing%20crisis%20is%20really%20worsening%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Mari%20Castaldi%2C%20director%20of%20state%20housing%20policy%20at%20the%20nonprofit%20Center%20on%20Budget%20and%20Policy%20Priorities%2C%20told%20Insider.%20She%20added%20of%20the%20city's%20mansion%20tax%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%20reasonable%20and%20equitable%20way%20to%20generate%20some%20resources%20that%20can%20support%20those%20needs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20some%20of%20the%20law's%20biggest%20proponents%20say%20it%20has%20a%20key%20flaw.%20Critics%20say%20the%20tax%20is%20likely%20disincentivizing%20the%20development%20of%20multi-family%20buildings%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20very%20construction%20that%20would%20boost%20the%20affordable%20housing%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUnintended%20consequences%20of%20a%20mansion%20tax%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EColloquially%20known%20as%20a%20mansion%20tax%2C%20United%20to%20House%20LA%20(Measure%20ULA)%20passed%20in%20November%202022%20with%2058%25%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELA's%20law%20has%20a%20slew%20of%20well-heeled%20and%20vocal%20critics.%20Real%20estate%20interest%20groups%20and%20others%20have%20filed%20two%20suits%20over%20the%20policy%2C%20but%20both%20have%20been%20dismissed.%20The%20court%20rulings%20will%20likely%20be%20appealed%2C%20and%20critics%20of%20the%20law%20are%20planning%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fopinion%2Fstory%2F2023-11-08%2Feditorial-how-about-if-people-stop-fighting-measure-ula-and-see-how-much-good-it%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eother%20ways%20to%20undermine%20it%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20for%20now%2C%20the%20tax%20is%20in%20effect%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20raise%20about%20%24150%20million%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELA%20is%20not%20the%20only%20city%20that's%20banking%20on%20high-end%20home%20sales%20to%20boost%20low-income%20housing%20efforts.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmansion-tax-nyc-revised-increase-changes-explainer-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbpp.org%2Fresearch%2Fstate-budget-and-tax%2Fstate-mansion-taxes-on-very-expensive-homes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWashington%3C%2Fa%3E%20both%20have%20state-wide%20mansion%20taxes%2C%20while%20the%20governor%20of%20Massachusetts%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bostonglobe.com%2F2023%2F10%2F20%2Fbusiness%2Fproposed-healey-real-estate-transaction-fee%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egave%20her%20blessing%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20municipalities%20that%20want%20to%20implement%20a%20transfer%20tax%20on%20high-value%20property.%20The%20Chicago%20city%20council%20also%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-10-31%2Fchicago-s-proposed-mansion-tax-faces-troubled-real-estate-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eadvanced%20a%20proposal%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20bump%20taxes%20on%20homes%20sold%20for%20more%20than%20%241%20million.%20Most%20recently%2C%20Santa%20Fe%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmansion-property-tax-housing-prices-millionaires-santa-fe-new-mexico-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Evoted%20for%20an%20additional%203%25%20tax%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20buyers%20will%20pay%20on%20homes%20over%20%241%20million%20as%20a%20way%20to%20raise%20funds%20for%20the%20city's%20affordable%20housing%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20LA%2C%20Mayor%20Karen%20Bass%20and%20the%20city%20council%20have%20already%20determined%20what%20this%20year's%20tax%20revenue%20will%20be%20spent%20on.%20The%20biggest%20chunk%20%E2%80%94%20%2456.8%20million%20%E2%80%94%20will%20go%20to%20affordable%20housing%20projects.%20Another%20%2430.4%20million%20will%20fund%20short-term%20assistance%20for%20tenants%20and%20small%20landlords.%20And%20%2423%20million%20will%20go%20to%20providing%20those%20facing%20eviction%20with%20representation%2C%20the%20LA%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fopinion%2Fstory%2F2023-11-08%2Feditorial-how-about-if-people-stop-fighting-measure-ula-and-see-how-much-good-it%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShane%20Phillips%2C%20a%20UCLA%20housing%20researcher%20whose%20work%20helped%20inspire%20LA's%20mansion%20tax%2C%20is%20worried%20about%20the%20mansion%20tax%20depressing%20new%20development%2C%20particularly%20of%20multi-family%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pushed%20for%20the%20policy%20to%20exempt%20first%20sales%20within%2010%20years%20of%20construction%20so%20that%20the%20tax%20doesn't%20disincentivize%20developers%2C%20who%20often%20sell%20apartment%20buildings%20soon%20after%20construction%20is%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20LA%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.calcities.org%2Fdocs%2Fdefault-source%2Fcity-attorneys%2F5.2023-spring-curtin_morrison_2022-housing-legislation-and-state-density-bonus-law.pdf%3Fsfvrsn%3D437bf36_3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20least%2010%25%20of%20units%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20multi-family%20buildings%20are%20designated%20for%20lower-income%20residents%2C%20meaning%20that%20if%20a%20number%20of%20new%20apartment%20buildings%20aren't%20built%20because%20of%20the%20tax%2C%20the%20city%20could%20end%20up%20losing%20a%20number%20of%20affordable%20units%20that%20are%20extremely%20expensive%20for%20the%20government%20to%20build%20or%20subsidize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20taxing%20these%20new%20buildings%20and%20the%20new%20buildings%20are%20maybe%20going%20to%20account%20for%20like%20five%20or%2010%25%20of%20total%20revenues%2C%20maybe%20%24100%20million%20at%20most%2C%20but%20we%20might%20lose%20a%20bunch%20of%20privately-built%20below-market%20units%20that%20will%20cost%20us%20more%20than%20%24100%20million%20to%20subsidize%2C%26quot%3B%20Phillips%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20like%2C%20what%20are%20we%20doing%20here%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhillips%20said%20transfer%20taxes%20are%20the%20%26quot%3Bthird-best%20real%20estate-related%20tax.%26quot%3B%20The%20best%20kind%20is%20a%20land%20value%20tax%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20because%20it%20both%20raises%20revenue%20and%20encourages%20the%20highest%20and%20best%20use%20of%20a%20piece%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second-most%20effective%20are%20property%20taxes%2C%20he%20said%2C%20as%20they%20can%20be%20collected%20regularly%2C%20instead%20of%20just%20when%20a%20property%20changes%20hands.%20But%20both%20of%20those%20are%20politically%20tricky%20in%20California%2C%20where%20property%20taxes%20are%20massively%20limited%20by%20the%20state's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcalmatters.org%2Fpolitics%2F2020%2F10%2Fprop-13-family-tree%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EProposition%2013%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETransfer%20taxes%20on%20expensive%20property%20sales%20have%20an%20admirable%20goal%3A%20redistributing%20some%20of%20the%20riches%20the%20real%20estate%20industry%20and%20homeowners%20have%20collected%20as%20home%20values%20have%20skyrocketed%20in%20recent%20years.%20And%2C%20when%20designed%20effectively%2C%20they%20can%20have%20a%20minimal%20chilling%20effect%20on%20the%20market%2C%20while%20raising%20significant%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20that's%20been%20made%20and%2C%20to%20an%20extent%2C%20trying%20to%20recapture%20a%20small%20share%20of%20that%20is%20a%20very%20reasonable%20goal%2C%20especially%20if%20that%20money%20is%20then%20spent%20on%20helping%20people%20who%20have%20been%20harmed%20by%20those%20prices%20increasing%2C%26quot%3B%20Phillips%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20April%201%2C%20it%20wasn't%20just%20the%20%26quot%3BSelling%20Sunset%26quot%3B%20agents%20who%20were%20scrambling.%20Sellers%20across%20LA%20did%20everything%20they%20could%20to%20unload%20their%20properties%20before%20the%20deadline%20hit%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theagencyre.com%2Fagent%2Fbilly-rose%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBilly%20Rose%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20co-founder%20of%20luxury%20real%20estate%20firm%20The%20Agency%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20the%20numbers%2C%20you'll%20definitely%20see%20a%20spike%20in%20activity%20that%20occurred%20in%20the%2030%2C%2060%2C%2090%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20April%201%2C%26quot%3B%20Rose%20said.%20And%20there%20were%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2023-03-27%2Flos-angeles-mansion-tax-owners-sell-homes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eofferings%20of%20cars%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20big%20commissions%20and%20various%20incentives%20to%20try%20to%20get%20a%20sale%20to%20take%20place%26quot%3B%20prior%20to%20implementation%2C%20he%20said%2C%20although%20he%20personally%20doesn't%20know%20of%20any%20situations%20where%20that%20actually%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERose%20said%20the%20new%20tax%2C%20coupled%20with%20high%20interest%20rates%2C%20is%20contributing%20to%20stagnation%20in%20the%20marketplace%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20just%20getting%20less%20and%20less%20available%20properties%20to%20sell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20chilling%20effect%20is%20likely%20temporary.%20Castaldi%20said%20the%20impact%20so%20far%20has%20been%20skewed%20by%20sellers%20delaying%20putting%20their%20properties%20on%20the%20market%20to%20see%20if%20the%20pending%20legal%20challenges%20would%20get%20the%20tax%20overturned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhillips%20isn't%20concerned%20about%20the%20short-term%20freeze%20in%20the%20high-end%20real%20estate%20market.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20he%20thinks%20owners%20who%20want%20to%20sell%20their%20properties%20will%20eventually%20do%20so%2C%20and%20the%20rate%20of%20transactions%20will%20be%20back%20to%20normal%20in%20about%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERose%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bcan%20understand%20why%20there%20are%20people%20who%20are%20sympathetic%20to%20taxing%20multimillionaires%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20the%20tax%20isn't%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20really%20sit%20with%20these%20wealthy%20people.%26quot%3B%20Instead%2C%20he%20said%2C%20it%20might%20fall%20on%20people%20struggling%20with%20inflation%20and%20trying%20to%20buy%20a%20home%2C%20especially%20with%20less%20construction%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20city%20finds%20that%20the%20mansion%20tax%20does%20disincentivize%20development%20and%20reduces%20the%20supply%20of%20affordable%20and%20market-rate%20housing%2C%20the%20city%20council%20could%20revise%20the%20law.%20Phillips%20argued%20that%20if%20the%20law%20is%20tweaked%20to%20exempt%20first-time%20sales%2C%20the%20mansion%20tax%20%26quot%3Bwill%20unquestionably%20do%20more%20good%20than%20harm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20tax%20has%20negative%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20Phillips%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20this%20one%20specific%20negative%20consequence%20we%20really%20need%20to%20solve%2C%20but%20other%20than%20that%20there%20are%20pretty%20limited%20consequences%20from%20a%20tax%20like%20this.%20And%20having%20%24700%20million%2C%20a%20billion%20dollars%20a%20year%20to%20spend%20on%20affordable%20housing%2C%20and%20rent%20assistance%2C%20and%20right-to-counsel%20and%20things%20like%20that%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20going%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fselling-sunset-los-angeles-mansion-tax-millionaires-housing-crisis-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699784521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e551e36d588dc55ce72d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fselling-sunset-los-angeles-mansion-tax-millionaires-housing-crisis-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20this%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BSelling%20Sunset%2C%26quot%3B%20there's%20a%20new%20villain%20in%20town.%20It's%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20mansion%20tax.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan%2CEliza%20Relman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fselling-sunset-los-angeles-mansion-tax-millionaires-housing-crisis-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20first%20to%20score%20more%20than%20500%20runs%20in%20two%20consecutive%20WCs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699784393000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105166527%2Cimgsize-49638.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Fworld-cup-rohit-sharma-becomes-first-player-to-score-more-than-500-runs-in-two-consecutive-editions%2Farticleshow%2F105166560.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20has%20been%20in%20superb%20form%20during%20the%20Worl