20about%20managing%20those%20workers%20in%20a%20way%20that%20makes%20the%20most%20of%20their%20time.%20Doing%20so%20can%20make%20it%20less%20likely%20that%20moms%20who%20work%20from%20home%20will%20miss%20out%20on%20key%20assignments%20or%20be%20left%20behind%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20career%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResendez%20told%20Insider%20that%20employers%20need%20to%20be%20deliberate%20about%20how%20they%20come%20up%20with%20their%20RTO%20policies%20so%20that%20moms%20aren't%20pushed%20out%20of%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20you%20create%20a%20return-to-work%20policy%2C%20really%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20assess%20the%20needs%20of%20that%20department%2C%20and%20then%20also%20survey%20the%20employees%20to%20understand%20the%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20open-minded%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMandy%20McAllister%2C%20CEO%20of%20GoBundance%20Women%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20women%20shouldn't%20feel%20like%20they%20can't%20talk%20to%20their%20bosses%20about%20their%20needs%2C%20but%20those%20who%20pitch%20a%20fix%20to%20a%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20like%20set%20RTO%20days%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0stand%20a%20better%20chance%20of%20getting%20a%20boss%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20workable%20setup%20for%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20any%20big%20problem%2C%20the%20one%20who%20comes%20up%20with%20the%20solution%20gets%20what%20they%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResendez%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20wait%20for%20someone%20to%20rescue%20us%2C%20if%20we%20wait%20for%20someone%20else%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20master%20plan%20for%20us%20to%20grow%20our%20career%20in%20spite%20of%20whatever%20situation%20we%20have%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20waiting%20for%20a%20really%20long%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EReally%20embrace%20the%20meaning%20of%20flexibility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKelly%20Scheib%2C%20chief%20people%20officer%20at%20dat