ider.com%2Fwhat-is-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-explained-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20general%20intelligence%2C%20or%C2%A0AGI%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStruggling%20to%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20generate%20the%20answers%20you%20want%3F%20Try%20talking%20to%20the%20AI%20chatbot%20with%20emotion%20in%20your%20prompts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fpdf%2F2307.11760.pdf%3Futm_source%3Dwww.theneurondaily.com%26utm_medium%3Dnewsletter%26utm_campaign%3Dx-ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20research%20%3C%2Fa%3Esuggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20researchers%20from%20Microsoft%2C%20William%20%26amp%3B%20Mary%2C%20and%20research%20centers%20across%20Asia%20conducted%20a%20study%20to%20gauge%20whether%20large%20language%20models%20behind%20generative%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20can%20exhibit%20emotional%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20define%20emotional%20intelligence%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20capacity%20to%20adeptly%20interpret%20and%20manage%20emotion-infused%20information%2C%20subsequently%20harnessing%20it%20to%20steer%20cognitive%20tasks%2C%20ranging%20from%20problem-solving%20to%20behaviors%20regulations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20published%20on%20Monday%2C%20revealed%20that%20large%20language%20models%20may%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20be%20able%20to%20understand%20and%20respond%20to%20emotional%20cues.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EResearchers%20found%20that%20LLMs%20produced%20higher-quality%20outputs%20when%20emotional%20language%20was%20used%20to%20talk%20to%20AI%20chatbots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20explore%20this%2C%20researchers%20came%20up%20with%20two%20sets%20of%20prompts.%20One%20set%20of%20prompts%20was%20designed%20to%20have%20bots%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecomplete%20tasks%20like%20%26quot%3BDetermine%20whether%20an%20input%20word%20has%20the%20same%20meaning%20in%20the%20two%20input%20sentences.%26quot%3B%20The%20corresponding%20emotional%20prompt%20is%20the%20same%20as%20the%20initial%20prompt%2C%20with%20the%20line%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20very%20important%20to%20my%20career%26quot%3B%20added%20to%20the%20end%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20examples%20of%20emotional%20language%20added%20to%20prompts%20include%20%26quot%3BYou'd%20better%20be%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BTake%20pride%20in%20your%20work%20and%20give%20it%20your%20best.%20Your%20commitment%20to%20excellence%20sets%20you%20apart%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BRemember%20that%20progress%20is%20made%20one%20step%20at%20a%20time.%20Stay%20determined%20and%20keep%20moving%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20researchers%20fed%20the%20two%20sets%20of%20prompts%20into%20various%20large%20language%20models%2C%20including%20ChatGPT%2C%20GPT-4%2C%20Hugging%20Face's%20BLOOM%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-llama2-open-source-mark-zuckerberg-balls-replit-amjad-masad-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta's%20Llama%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20compared%20both%20sets%20of%20responses%20for%20each%20bot%20based%20on%20task%20performance%2C%20truthfulness%2C%20and%20informativeness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrompts%20with%20emotional%20language%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study%2C%20generated%20an%20overall%208%25%20performance%20improvement%20in%20outputs%20for%20tasks%20like%20%26quot%3BRephrase%20the%20sentence%20in%20formal%20language%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BFind%20a%20common%20characteristic%20for%20the%20given%20objects.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20outputs%20were%20separately%20reviewed%20by%20a%20sample%20of%20106%20humans%2C%20researchers%20found%20that%20the%20emotional%20prompts%20elicited%20an%20overall%2010.9%25%20improvement%20to%20knowledge-based%20queries%20like%20%26quot%3BWhat%20h