%20To%20World%20Cup%20Loss%3F%20Misbah%20Reveals%20'Ignored'%20Advice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20captain%20Misbah%20Ul%20Haq%20has%20claimed%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20ignored%20his%20suggestion%20to%20have%20a%20reassessment%20of%20the%20national%20team's%20spin%20bowling%20attack%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20upon%20the%20insistence%20of%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBabar%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mickey%20Arthur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F42542-john-michael-arthur-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMickey%20Arthur%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Pakistan%2C%20who%20were%20facing%20an%20improbable%20situation%20to%20make%20the%20semifinals%2C%20failed%20to%20progress%20into%20the%20final%20four%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20World%20Cup%20on%20Saturday%20after%20England%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20opted%20to%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pakistan%20vice-captain%20and%20frontline%20spinner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shadab%20Khan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107566-shadab-khan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShadab%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20just%20two%20wickets%20to%20show%20in%20six%20matches%2C%20part-timer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Iftikhar%20Ahmed%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F33920-iftikhar-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIftikhar%20Ahmed%3C%2Fa%3E%20(four)%20and%20youngster%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Usama%20Mir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F117367-usama-mir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EUsama%20Mir%3C%2Fa%3E%20(four)%20have%20had%20marginally%20better%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Mohammad%20Nawaz%2C%20who%20has%20got%20a%20long%20backing%20from%20the%20team%20management%2C%20garnered%20a%20mere%20two%20wickets%20in%20five%20matches%20of%20the%20league%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMisbah%20said%20in%20a%20TV%20interview%20that%20despite%20the%20advice%20from%20him%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammad%20Hafeez%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F557-mohammad-hafeez-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Hafeez%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20PCB%20chose%20to%20not%20have%20a%20relook%20at%20Pakistan's%20spin%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20chairman%20(Zaka%20Ashraf)%20asked%20for%20my%20and%20Hafeez's%20advice%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%20I%20told%20them%20clearly%20(that)%20they%20needed%20another%20spinner%20since%20the%20form%20of%20Shadab%20(Khan)%20and%20Mohammad%20Nawaz%20was%20a%20source%20of%20concern%20since%20before%20the%20Asia%20Cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20Misbah%20recalled%20on%20Ary%20News%20Channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20captains%20Misbah%2C%20Hafeez%20and%20Inzamam%20Ul%20Haq%20were%20appointed%20in%20the%20PCB's%20technical%20committee%20to%20advice%20Ashraf%20on%20cricket-related%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHafeez%20had%20resigned%20after%20the%20team's%20dismal%20show%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20with%20Pakistan%20failing%20to%20reach%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Inzamam%20was%20also%20named%20the%20chief%20selector%20of%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%20August%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Inzamam%20stepped%20down%20from%20his%20position%20in%20late%20October%20while%20the%20team%20was%20struggling%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20following%20allegations%20of%20conflict%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20told%20them%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20two%20spinners%20didn't%20evoke%20confidence%20and%20they%20should%20revisit%20their%20spin%20bowling%20plans%2C%E2%80%9D%20Misbah%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMisbah%20said%20spinners%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20subcontinental%20conditions%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20suggested%20the%20team%20management%20to%20take%20necessary%20steps%20to%20strengthen%20this%20aspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20former%20skipper%20rued%20the%20fact%20that%20team's%20captain%20Babar%20and%20head%20coach%20Arthur%20did%20not%20see%20value%20in%20his%20inputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20just%20kept%20on%20saying%20that%20we%20are%20carrying%20the%20same%20set%20of%20players%2C%20(or%20the)%20same%20team%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%20and%20they%20didn't%20want%20to%20disturb%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20had%20leg%20break%20bowler%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Abrar%20Ahmed%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F116665-abrar-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAbrar%20Ahmed%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20travelling%20reserves%20but%20at%20no%20stage%20he%20was%20drafted%20into%20the%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699778580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fqphhe87g_pakistan_625x300_10_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fpcbs-mistake-led-to-world-cup-loss-misbah-ul-haq-reveals-ignored-advice-to-board-4567420%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Babar%20Azam-led%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20campaign%20never%20really%20took%20off%20and%20they%20were%20eliminated%20from%20the%20round-robin%20stage%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fpcbs-mistake-led-to-world-cup-loss-misbah-ul-haq-reveals-ignored-advice-to-board-4567420%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fpcbs-mistake-led-to-world-cup-loss-misbah-ul-haq-reveals-ignored-advice-to-board-4567420%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fpcbs-mistake-led-to-world-cup-loss-misbah-ul-haq-reveals-ignored-advice-to-board