ading%20them%2C%20it's%20more%20about%20how%20this%20team%20wants%20to%20be%20led.%20What%20about%20the%20system%2C%20how%20do%20they%20approach%20the%20white%20ball%20cricket%3F%20What%20are%20the%20fault-lines%2C%20where%20are%20they%20so%20irrelevant%20at%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20Rameez%20Raja%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20Babar%20Azam%20has%20been%20advised%20against%20putting%20in%20his%20papers%20by%20his%20national%20teammates%20even%20as%20he%20has%20rested%20case%20with%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20headed%20by%20Zaka%20Ashraf%20to%20take%20a%20call%20on%20his%20future.%20Pakistan%20finished%20fifth%20in%2010%20team%20table%20and%20missed%20out%20on%20semi-final%20qualification%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism%20from%20former%20players%2C%20who%20has%20sought%20a%20change%20in%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBabar%20has%20already%20spoken%20to%20his%20teammates%2C%20and%20majority%20of%20them%20advised%20him%20not%20to%20step%20down%20himself.%20He%20will%20come%20out%20with%20a%20clear%20line%20of%20action%20once%20he%20returns%20home%20with%20the%20team%20after%20failing%20to%20make%20the%20semi-finals%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20India.%20But%2C%20he%20will%20not%20step%20down%20himself%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20PCB%20source%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabar%20has%20a%20strong%20following%20in%20the%20team%20and%20likes%20of%20Imam%20ul%20Haq%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shadab%20Khan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107566-shadab-khan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShadab%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Haris%20Rauf%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112775-haris-rauf-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHaris%20Rauf%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20players%20considered%20to%20be%20close%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20skipper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20last%20year%20wh