.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20praised%20Kherson%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcity%20of%20hope%26quot%3B%20while%20regretting%20%26quot%3Brevenge%26quot%3B%20daily%20shelling%20by%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20between%20yesterday%20evening%20and%20this%20morning%2C%20(Russia%20launched)%20almost%2040%20drones%20and%20rockets...%20Ballistic%20attacks%20against%20Kyiv%2C%20drones%2C%20and%20rockets%20against%20Odesa%2C%20the%20Kharkiv%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20been%20bracing%20for%20a%20renewed%20aerial%20onslaught%20this%20winter%2C%20after%20systematic%20strikes%20on%20the%20country's%20energy%20grid%20left%20thousands%20without%20heating%20or%20electricity%20in%20freezing%20temperatures%20last%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20missile%20targeted%20Kyiv%20%26quot%3Bafter%20a%20long%20pause%20of%2052%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Kyiv%20city%20military%20administration%20Sergiy%20Popko.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFP%20journalists%20in%20central%20Kyiv%20had%20heard%20two%20strong%20explosions%20and%20saw%20trails%20in%20the%20sky%20at%20dawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20sirens%20had%20sounded%20soon%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20force%20said%20it%20destroyed%20a%20missile%20approaching%20Kyiv%20--%20either%20an%20Iskander%20ballistic%20missile%20or%20an%20S-400%20anti-aircraft%20missile%20--%20without%20reporting%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20defences%20last%20downed%20a%20missile%20in%20Kyiv%20on%20September%2021.%20The%20falling%20debris%20wounded%20seven%20people%2C%20including%20a%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrone%20Attacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20missiles%20hit%20a%20field%20between%20two%20settlements%20in%20the%20wider%20Kyiv%20region%2C%20damaging%20five%20private%20homes%2C%20said%20regional%20military%20administration%20chief%20Ruslan%20Kravchenko%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20force%20said%20it%20downed%2019%20of%20the%2031%20attack%20drones%20launched%20by%20Moscow%20between%20Friday%20evening%20and%20Saturday%2003%3A00%20am%20(0100%20GMT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Russian%20occupants%20sent%20most%20of%20the%20attack%20UAVs%20to%20the%20frontline%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20Russia%20fired%20several%20missiles%20overnight%2C%20but%20did%20not%20specify%20if%20any%20were%20downed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20two%20men%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20northeast%20region%20of%20Sumy%20in%20an%20unspecified%20Russian%20attack%2C%20according%20to%20the%20prosecutor%20general's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20missiles%20also%20hit%20Odesa%2C%20wounding%20three%20people%20including%20a%2096-year-old%20woman%20who%20was%20hospitalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainians%20have%20worried%20that%20Russia%20may%20pick%20up%20its%20campaign%20of%20strikes%20on%20energy%20infrastructures%2C%20and%20warned%20Kyiv%20would%20strike%20back%20on%20Russian%20oil%20and%20gas%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnergy%20Minister%20German%20Galushchenko%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bwould%20be%20fair%26quot%3B%20to%20target%20Russia's%20oil%20and%20gas%20infrastructure%20if%20Ukraine's%20power%20grid%20came%20under%20sustained%20attacks%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Politico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prepare%20for%20the%20possible%20attacks%20on%20energy%20facilities%20--%20for%20a%20second%20winter%20--%20Zelensky%20said%20Tuesday%20Ukraine%20had%20deployed%20more%20defence%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'City%20Of%20Hope'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20also%20praised%20his%20country's%20resilience%20in%20a%20message%20congratulating%20residents%20and%20soldiers%20for%20the%20liberation%20of%20Kherson%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20the%20region%20of%20the%20same%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUkraine%20always%20comes%20back%20--%20always!%26quot%3B%20Zelensky%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20we%20are%20united.%20And%20when%20we%20unite%20others.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20forces%20liberated%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Kherson%20last%20November%2C%20routing%20Russian%20troops%20in%20an%20embarrassing%20defeat%20for%20the%20Kremlin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20forces%20based%20across%20the%20river%20from%20Kherson%20city%20still%20control%20swathes%20of%20territory%20and%20shell%20towns%20and%20villages%20they%20retreated%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20people%20died%20in%20Kherson%20and%20eight%20others%20were%20wounded%20over%20the%20past%20day%2C%20governor%20Oleksandr%20Prokudin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20troops%20also%20struck%20the%20central%20part%20of%20Kherson%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20wounding%20two%20people%2C%20the%20regional%20administration%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ground%2C%20Ukrainian%20forces%20are%20facing%20assaults%20from%20Russian%20troops%20around%20the%20eastern%20frontline%20town%20of%20Avdiivka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20servicemen%20and%20women%20are%20steadfastly%20holding%20the%20line%20in%20the%20Avdiivka%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20Ukrainian%20army%20commander%20Oleksandr%20Tarnavskyi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20officials%20said%20earlier%20this%20week%20they%20were%20bracing%20for%20a%20third%20wave%20of%20attacks%20from%20Russian%20forces%2C%20which%20began%20storming%20Avdiivka%20about%20a%20month%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20north%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Toretsk%2C%20two%20elderly%20people%20died%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20as%20a%20result%20of%20artillery%20fire%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20Ukraine's%20Prosecutor%20General.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699775100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fh4fkn00g_ukraine-war_625x300_12_November_