members%20of%20the%20UN%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20in%20Geneva.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2010%2C%20Canada%20underwent%20the%20UPR%20process%20for%20the%20fourth%20time%2C%20receiving%20evaluations%20from%20the%20UPR%20working%20group%2C%20consisting%20of%20all%20UNHRC%20members.%20Canada%20was%20among%20the%2014%20countries%20reviewed%20during%20the%20current%20session.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20offered%20three%20suggestions%20to%20Canada%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20spirit%20of%20constructive%20dialogue%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COne%2C%20further%20strengthen%20the%20domestic%20framework%20to%20prevent%20misuse%20of%20freedom%20of%20expression%20for%20inciting%20violence%20and%20disallow%20activities%20of%20groups%20which%20are%20promoting%20extremism%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.un.org%2Fen%2Fasset%2Fk14%2Fk14bhl5fi4%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20Indian%20diplomat%20Mohammed%20Hussain%20K.S%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20called%20on%20Canada%20to%20%E2%80%9Ceffectively%20prevent%20attacks%20on%20places%20of%20worships%20of%20religious%20and%20racial%20minorities%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cstrengthen%20legislative%20and%20other%20measures%20to%20address%20hate%20crimes%20and%20hate%20speech%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThird%2C%20put%20an%20end%20to%20structural%20discrimination%20against%20children%20belonging%20to%20indigenous%20groups.%20And%20address%20disparities%20in%20access%20to%20services%20by%20all%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20the%20Indian%20representative.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20publicly%20accused%20India%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Sikh%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20relations%20have%20gone%20into%20deep%20freeze.%20Both%20countries%20ex