%20investigation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20previous%20UPR%20cycle%20that%20Canada%20underwent%20in%202018%2C%20India%20put%20forth%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmindiaun.gov.in%2Fpageinfo%2FMTY1Mw%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esix%20recommendations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20had%20also%20included%20calling%20for%20prevention%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmisuse%20of%20freedom%20of%20expression%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cglorify%5Bing%5D%20terrorists%20as%20martyrs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699765135000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F23142706%2F5553604787_a38f04d388_k1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Funhrc-india-canada-universal-periodic-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Member%20states%20of%20the%20UN%20undergo%20a%20periodic%20evaluation%20of%20their%20human%20rights%20records%20by%20the%2047%20members%20of%20the%20UN%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20in%20Geneva.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Funhrc-india-canada-universal-periodic-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Skating%20on%20a%20once-in-a-decade%20'ice%20window'%20in%20Alaska%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699763618000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FA03C%2Fproduction%2F_131702014_p0gs6t6p.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67394816%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Footage%20shows%20an%20ice%20rescue%20instructor%20skating%20on%20a%20rare%20window%20of%20ice%20in%20Alaska's%20Alpine%20lakes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A365%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-us-canada-67394816%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Resi