%20missing%20because%20of%20an%20effort%20at%20sanitising%20his%20prolific%20output.%20Pyarelal%2C%20his%20long-time%20personal%20secretary%2C%20is%20recorded%20telling%20the%20writer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyalebooks.yale.edu%2Fbook%2F9780300055399%2Fmahatma-gandhi-and-his-apostles%2F%5C%22%3EVed%20Mehta%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20%E2%80%9Cportentously%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20in%20the%20vastness%20of%20material%20he%20was%20holding%20in%20trust%2C%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Csome%E2%80%9D%20he%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%9Csuppress%E2%80%9D%2C%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9CGandhi%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20Israel%E2%80%9D.%20There%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20believe%20that%20Pyarelal%20has%20been%20inaccurately%20recorded%20in%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%201976%20book%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20rather%20cocky%20claim%20by%20Pyarelal%2C%20who%20died%20in%201982%2C%20that%20he%20held%20a%20unique%20power%20to%20decide%20how%20the%20public%20sees%20Gandhi%2C%20since%20%E2%80%9Cby%20God%E2%80%99s%20grace%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20only%20one%20who%20knows%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKumaraswamy%20concludes%20that%20we%20are%20left%20%E2%80%9Conly%20with%20a%20sanitised%20and%20politically%20correct%20version%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20means%20we%20will%20never%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20understand%20how%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20viewed%20and%20gradually%20shifted%20his%20position%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20Palestine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20more%20to%20say%3A%20Gandhi%20is%20known%20to%20have%20met%20two%20Zionist%20leaders%20when%20he%20went%20to%20London%20for%20the%20Second%20Round%20Table%20Conference%20on%20India.%20But%20the%20record%20of%20these%20meetings%20is%20missing%20from%20his%20Collected%20Works.%20There%20is%20in%20fact%2C%20a%20complete%20absence%20of%20any%20record%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20numerous%20meetings%20with%20Jewish%20leaders.%20Absence%20of%20evidence%2C%20he%20concludes%2C%20is%20not%20evidence%20of%20absence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20these%20scattershot%20insinuations%2C%20Kumaraswamy%20does%20draw%20attention%20to%20a%20specific%20absence.%20In%20July%201937%2C%20%E2%80%9CGandhi%20passed%20on%20an%20unsigned%20statement%20to%20the%20Jewish%20Agency%20in%20Palestine%20through%20Hermann%20Kallenbach%2C%20his%20comrade-in-arms%20during%20his%20South%20African%20days%E2%80%9D.%20This%20has%20gone%20%E2%80%9Cconspicuously%20missing%20in%20volume%2096%20of%20the%20Collected%20Works%2C%20devoted%20exclusively%20to%20the%20Kallenbach%20Papers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGandhi%20and%20Kallenbach%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20conspiratorially%20minded%2C%20the%20point%20may%20seem%20significant%2C%20though%20ultimately%20it%20is%20of%20little%20consequence.%20Kallenbach%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20India%20in%201937%20and%20his%20very%20fond%20reunion%20with%20Gandhi%20after%2023%20years%2C%20is%20dealt%20with%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGreat_Soul%3A_Mahatma_Gandhi_and_His_Struggle_with_India%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJoseph%20Lelyveld%E2%80%99s%202008%20book%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGreat%20Soul%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20was%20by%20all%20accounts%20a%20joyous%20moment%20for%20both%20men%2C%20but%20Kallenbach%20also%20came%20with%20a%20political%20mandate%20from%20the%20Jewish%20Agency%20for%20Palestine%2C%20the%20principal%20global%20body%20promoting%20the%20Zionist%20cause.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20was%20aware%20of%20Kallenbach%E2%80%99s%20Zionist%20affinity%20from%20their%20days%20together%20at%20Tolstoy%20Farm%20in%20South%20Africa.%20On%20February%2013%2C%201913%2C%20well%20before%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20epochal%20return%20to%20India%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gandhiheritageportal.org%2Fcwmg_volume_thumbview%2FOTY%3D%23page%2F144%2Fmode%2F2up%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Kallenbach%2C%20addressing%20some%20obvious%20dilemmas.%20%E2%80%9CI%20see%20that%20you%20are%20very%20unhappy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20but%20the%20remedy%20lay%20neither%20in%20%E2%80%9CPalestine%2C%20nor%20in%20studies%20in%20London%E2%80%9D.%20It%20was%20to%20be%20sought%2C%20rather%2C%20in%20one%20of%20two%20things%3A%20%E2%80%9Ceither%20in%20applying%20yourself%20entirely%20to%20your%20office%20and%20studying%20whilst%20in%20practice%20or%20in%20your%20living%20with%20me%20and%20coming%20to%20India%E2%80%9D.%20And%20then%20came%20a%20stricture%20to%20not%20be%20led%20astray%20by%20shallow%20materiality%2C%20since%20you%20%E2%80%9Ccannot%20serve%20God%20and%20Mammon%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%5B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gandhiheritageportal.org%2Fcwmg_volume_thumbview%2FOTY%3D%23page%2F30%2Fmode%2F2up%5C%22%3ECollected%20Works%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20hereafter%20CWMG%2C%20Volume%2096%3A%20289%3C%2Fa%3E%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09163104%2FSchlesin_Gandhi_and_Kallenbach_after_the_Great_March.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22711%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09163104%2FSchlesin_Gandhi_and_Kallenbach_after_the_Great_March.png%20711w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09163104%2FSchlesin_Gandhi_and_Kallenbach_after_the_Great_March-300x276.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684303%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22655%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESonja%20Schlesin%2C%20M.K.%20Gandhi%20and%20Hermann%20Kallenbach.%20Photo%3A%20Unknown%20author%2C%20Public%20Domain%20via%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20deeply%20personal%20communication%20was%20from%20a%20time%20before%20Zionism%20gained%20the%20backing%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20colonial%20power.%20The%20Balfour%20Declaration%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opendemocracy.net%2Fen%2Fzionism-anti-semitism-and-balfour-declaration%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20testament%20to%20European%20Anti-Semitism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20was%20still%20a%20few%20years%20in%20the%20future%2C%20and%20Zionism%20seemed%20an%20attractive%20option%20for%20youth%20fighting%20a%20sense%20of%20alienation%20as%20the%20world%20plunged%20towards%20the%20catastrophe%20of%201914.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELittle%20else%20of%20any%20pertinence%20transpired%20between%20the%20two%20friends%20till%20Kallenbach%20called%20on%20Gandhi%20in%201937.%20As%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGreat-Soul-Mahatma-Gandhi-Struggle%2Fdp%2F0307389952%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELelyveld%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2008%3A%20279)%20tells%20it%2C%20Kallenbach%20had%20earlier%20been%20contacted%20by%20Moshe%20Shertok%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Political%20Department%20of%20the%20Jewish%20Agency%20in%20Palestine%20(who%20in%201954%20became%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister%20for%20a%20brief%20term).%20Shertok%E2%80%99s%20purpose%20was%20to%20seek%20a%20connection%20to%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20greatest%20of%20living%20Hindus%E2%80%9D.%20Gaining%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20endorsement%2C%20Shertok%20wrote%2C%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cservice%20of%20an%20extraordinary%20character%E2%80%9D%20that%20Kallenbach%20alone%20would%20be%20able%20to%20render%20because%20of%20his%20%E2%80%9Cunique%20position%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20months%20before%20Kallenbach%20landed%20in%20India%20in%20May%201937%2C%20he%20travelled%20to%20London%20to%20meet%20with%20Shertok%20and%20Chaim%20Weizmann%2C%20a%20future%20president%20of%20Israel.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20Palestine%20and%20spent%20time%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekibbutz%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20seemingly%20finding%20a%20close%20affinity%20between%20its%20culture%20and%20the%20principles%20Gandhi%20had%20fostered%20in%20Tolstoy%20farm.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20docked%20in%20Bombay%2C%20Kallenbach%20hurried%20off%20his%20ship%20to%20the%20village%20in%20Gujarat%20where%20Gandhi%20was%20at%20the%20time.%20The%20two%20friends%20spent%20much%20of%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20in%20Lelyveld%E2%80%99s%20account%2C%20in%20conversations%20on%20the%20strife%20in%20Palestine.%20There%20was%20for%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20%E2%80%9Ceagerly%20entered%20into%20the%20conversations%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20religious%20principle%20involved.%20Hindus%20in%20India%2C%20he%20believed%2C%20were%20obliged%20to%20support%20the%20Muslim%20cause.%20Kallenbach%20urged%20%E2%80%9Csympathetic%20attention%20to%20the%20Zionist%20side%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20their%20dialogue%20was%20inconclusive.%20It%20resumed%20in%20an%20exchange%20of%20correspondence%20after%20they%20parted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2020%2C%20Gandhi%20wrote%20from%20his%20Wardha%20ashram%2C%20telling%20Kallenbach%20how%20much%20he%20is%20missed.%20He%20then%20refers%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9CPalestine%20Report%E2%80%9D%20which%20makes%20%E2%80%9Csad%20reading%E2%80%9D%2C%20though%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Commission%E2%80%9D%20perhaps%20could%20do%20nothing%20more.%20The%20context%20makes%20clear%20that%20he%20is%20referring%20to%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Royal%20Commission%20on%20Palestine%20under%20Robert%20Peel%2C%20appointed%20to%20enquire%20into%20months%20of%20civil%20unrest%20against%20Jewish%20colonisation.%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20main%20conclusion%20from%20his%20reading%20of%20the%20report%20was%20that%20it%20was%20clear%20admission%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinitial%20blunder%E2%80%9D%20of%20making%20one%20%E2%80%9Cpromise%20to%20the%20Arabs%20and%20a%20contrary%20one%20to%20the%20Jews%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Peel%20Commission%20Report%20was%20effective%20admission%20that%20the%20League%20of%20Nations%20mandate%20for%20Palestine%20that%20Britain%20had%20secured%20was%20unworkable.%20It%20was%20perhaps%20the%20first%20inkling%20of%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20intent%20to%20scuttle%20and%20run%20from%20an%20unmanageable%20situation%20of%20its%20own%20creation.%20In%20the%20circumstances%2C%20Gandhi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gandhiheritageportal.org%2Fcwmg_volume_thumbview%2FOTY%3D%23page%2F322%2Fmode%2F2up%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Conly%20proper%20and%20dignified%20solution%E2%80%9D%20was%20for%20the%20Jews%20to%20%E2%80%9Crely%20wholly%20on%20the%20Arab%20goodwill%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Conce%20and%20for%20all%20renounce%20British%20protection%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%5B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gandhiheritageportal.org%2Fcwmg_volume_thumbview%2FOTY%3D%23page%2F30%2Fmode%2F2up%5C%22%3ECWMG%2C%20Volume%2096%3A%20289%3C%2Fa%3E%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20fond%20hope%20was%20detached%20from%20reality%20since%20the%20Jewish%20settlers%20in%20Palestine%20were%20working%20with%20British%20colonial%20authorities%20to%20brutally%20crush%20the%20uprising.%20Kallenbach%20however%2C%20was%20not%20abandoning%20his%20mission%20of%20persuasion.%20Soon%20afterwards%20he%20obtained%20from%20the%20Jewish%20Agency%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctwenty-five%20page%20essay%20on%20the%20historic%2C%20spiritual%20and%20political%20underpinnings%20of%20Zionism%E2%80%9D%2C%20specially%20written%20for%20Gandhi%20(Lelyveld%2C%202008%3A%20278).%20Though%20a%20little%20puzzled%20by%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20sender%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20Gandhi%20found%20the%20essay%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20impressive%2C%20deeply%20interesting%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20thought%20that%20if%20the%20points%20made%20were%20true%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20settlement%20between%20the%20Jews%20and%20the%20Arabs%20ought%20not%20to%20be%20difficult%E2%80%9D%20%5BCWMG%2C%2096%3A%20290%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGandhi%3A%20%E2%80%98a%20prisoner%20of%20hope%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20where%20Gandhi%20perhaps%20lives%20up%20to%20his%20image%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprisoner%20of%20hope%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20the%20British%20scholar%2C%20Judith%20Brown%2C%20described%20him%20many%20years%20later.%20In%20the%20twisted%20context%20of%20geopolitics%20playing%20out%20in%20Palestine%2C%20he%20actually%20thought%20of%20a%20mediatory%20role%2C%20with%20Kallenbach%E2%80%99s%20intercession%20being%20essential.%20%E2%80%9CI%20quite%20clearly%20see%20that%20if%20you%20are%20to%20play%20any%20part%20in%20bringing%20about%20an%20honourable%20settlement%2C%20your%20place%20is%20in%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20might%20have%20to%20go%20frequently%20to%20Palestine%20but%20much%20of%20the%20work%20lies%20in%20India%20as%20I%20visualize%20the%20development%20of%20the%20settlement%20talks.%E2%80%9D%20%5B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gandhiheritageportal.org%2Fcwmg_volume_thumbview%2FOTY%3D%23page%2F30%2Fmode%2F2up%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECWMG%2C%2096%3A%20290%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%5D%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20next%20time%20the%20issue%20comes%20up%20between%20the%20two%20friends%20is%20in%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20letter%20of%20October%2011%2C%20when%20he%20writes%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Palestine%20question%20does%20now%20engage%20my%20attention.%20It%20is%20becoming%20more%20and%20more%20intricate%20for%20want%20of%20a%20firm%20declaration%20such%20as%20I%20have%20suggested.%20But%20that%20will%20never%20come%20unless%20there%20is%20an%20urge%20from%20within%E2%80%9D.%20Perhaps%2C%20Gandhi%20writes%2C%20when%20Kallenbach%20arrives%20on%20his%20planned%20visit%20to%20India%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20they%20could%20%E2%80%9Cexplore%20possibilities%E2%80%9D%20%5BCWMG%2C%2096%3A%20291%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKallenbach%E2%80%99s%20visit%20does%20not%20materialise%2C%20which%20disappoints%20Gandhi.%20The%20next%20time%20the%20issue%20comes%20up%20between%20the%20friends%2C%20all%20optimism%20seems%20dissipated.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20a%20tragedy%20going%20on%20in%20Palestine!%E2%80%9D%2C%20writes%20Gandhi%20on%20July%2017%2C%201938%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20heart-breaking.%20If%20there%20is%20peace%2C%20ultimately%2C%20it%20will%20be%20the%20peace%20of%20the%20grave.%20However%2C%20we%20must%20endure%20what%20we%20cannot%20cure%E2%80%9D%20%5BCWMG%2C%2096%3A%20295%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELelyveld%20fills%20in%20the%20missing%20details%20in%20this%20record%20of%20correspondence%2C%20revealing%20in%20itself.%20Following%20their%20conversations%20in%201937%20and%20Kallenbach%E2%80%99s%20educational%20efforts%2C%20Gandhi%20sent%20a%20draft%20set%20of%20proposals%20to%20his%20friend.%20Unconvinced%2C%20Kallenbach%20sent%20these%20on%20to%20Chaim%20Weizmann.%20Conversations%20ended%20there%2C%20since%20the%20Jewish%20Agency%20chose%20to%20suppress%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20proposals%20%5BLelyveld%2C%202008%3A%20280%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20affords%20scope%20for%20a%20robust%20inference%2C%20far%20from%20the%20conspiracy%20theory%20Kumaraswamy%20hints%20at.%20The%20paper%20which%20he%20alleges%20was%20banished%20into%20a%20memory%20hole%2C%20was%20obviously%20not%20what%20the%20Zionist%20camp%20expected%20when%20they%20tasked%20Kallenbach%20with%20his%20mission.%20The%20%E2%80%9Cworld%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20Hindu%E2%80%9D%20was%20not%20about%20to%20sign%20on%20for%20the%20Jewish%20colonisation%20of%20Palestine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDid%20the%20Holocaust%20impact%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20views%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKumaraswamy%20has%20another%20revelation%20to%20make%2C%20this%20one%20virtually%20impossible%20to%20verify%2C%20but%20circumstantially%20suspect.%20The%20time%20is%20June%201946%2C%20and%20grisly%20and%20horrifying%20details%20of%20the%20Holocaust%20have%20come%20to%20light.%20That%20may%20have%20been%20the%20background%20condition%2C%20he%20posits%2C%20for%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20conversion.%20At%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20American%20journalist%20Louis%20Fischer%2C%20later%20author%20of%20one%20of%20the%20first%20biographies%20of%20the%20Mahatma%2C%20Gandhi%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Jews%20have%20a%20good%20cause.%20I%20told%20(British%20Zionist%20MP)%20Sidney%20Silverman%20that%20the%20Jews%20have%20a%20good%20case%20in%20Palestine.%20If%20the%20Arabs%20have%20a%20claim%20to%20Palestine%2C%20the%20Jews%20have%20a%20prior%20claim%E2%80%9D.%20Louis%20Fischer%E2%80%99s%201947%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20and%20Stalin%3A%20Two%20Signs%20at%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Crossroads%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20records%20this%20supposed%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFischer%E2%80%99s%20book%20is%20inaccessible%20at%20this%20time%2C%20and%20the%20quote%20and%20context%20cannot%20be%20verified.%20Kumaraswamy%20concedes%20another%20interpretation%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20but%20backs%20Fischer%E2%80%99s%20account%20since%20it%20was%20published%20during%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20lifetime.%20This%20alleged%20quote%20has%20also%20been%20put%20forward%20by%20Khinvraj%20Jangid%20in%20an%20article%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fisrael-first-prime-minister-gandhi-portrait-9006163%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVerification%20here%20is%20very%20easy.%20The%20Jewish%20Virtual%20Library%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jewishvirtuallibrary.org%2Fgandhi-discussion-with-mr-silverman-and-mr-honick-on-jews-and-arabs-march-1946%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epresents%20a%20paraphrase%20of%20the%20discussion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20between%20Gandhi%20and%20Silverman%20in%20June%201946%2C%20which%20in%20turn%2C%20is%20sourced%20from%20the%20Louis%20Fischer%20papers.%20It%20shows%20Gandhi%20eagerly%20questioning%20his%20interlocutors%20on%20the%20Jewish%20claim%20for%20a%20homeland%20in%20Palestine%2C%20though%20he%20begins%20with%20the%20plea%20that%20he%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20do%20very%20much%20for%20them.%20Despite%20all%20the%20%E2%80%9Csympathy%E2%80%9D%20he%20may%20have%20for%20the%20cause%2C%20he%20found%20much%20that%20was%20wrong%20in%20the%20methods%20that%20Zionism%20had%20adopted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESilverman%20blamed%20all%20the%20violence%20on%20%E2%80%9Ca%20small%20section%20of%20terrorist%20hotheads%E2%80%9D%2C%20admitting%20much%20that%20was%20wrong%20about%20the%20Zionist%20campaign%20in%20Palestine.%20Beyond%20the%20legalities%2C%20Silverman%20urged%20that%20the%20moral%20question%20be%20addressed.%20If%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccrazy%20(sic)%20vessel%20bringing%20Jewish%20refugees%20comes%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20shore%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said%20with%20some%20warmth%2C%20it%20would%20seem%20the%20humane%20thing%20to%20%E2%80%9Chelp%20in%20getting%20them%20ashore%E2%80%9D%2C%20rather%20than%20%E2%80%9Cshoot%20them%20down%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20clear%20references%20to%20the%20ships%20bringing%20survivors%20of%20Nazi%20concentration%20camps%20to%20what%20would%20putatively%2C%20be%20their%20new%20home.%20Britain%2C%20still%20retaining%20its%20League%20of%20Nations%20mandate%20over%20Palestine%20and%20burdened%20by%20its%20duplicity%2C%20had%20prohibited%20Jewish%20immigration%20in%201939.%20Ships%20carrying%20European%20Jews%20to%20Palestine%20were%20turned%20away%2C%20triggering%20a%20savage%20assault%20on%20the%20British%20administration%20by%20terrorist%20gangs%20led%20by%20Menachem%20Begin%20and%20Yitzhak%20Shamir%20(both%20future%20prime%20ministers).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09164934%2F1024px-Flickr_-_Government_Press_Office_GPO_-_P.M._Menahem_Begin.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09164934%2F1024px-Flickr_-_Government_Press_Office_GPO_-_P.M._Menahem_Begin.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09164934%2F1024px-Flickr_-_Government_Press_Office_GPO_-_P.M._Menahem_Begin-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMenahem%20Begin%20and%20Yitzhak%20Shamir.%20Photo%3A%20Government%20Press%20Office%20(Israel)%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20offers%20sympathy%20but%20nothing%20substantive.%20He%20asks%20about%20the%20Zionist%20insistence%20on%20a%20homeland%20in%20Palestine%20rather%20than%20elsewhere.%20Silverman%20claims%20the%20right%20of%20ownership%20from%20the%20presence%20of%20650%2C000%20Jews%20in%20Palestine%2C%20who%20had%20transformed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwaste%20space%E2%80%9D%20that%20%E2%80%9Cno%20one%20else%20wanted%E2%80%9D.%20Jews%20were%20only%20seeking%20to%20%E2%80%9Cregain%20what%20(they%20had)%20lost%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20the%20Arabs%20stood%20to%20lose%20nothing.%20Gandhi%20was%20unconvinced%2C%20asking%20if%20that%20meant%20the%20reduction%20of%20Arabs%20to%20a%20minority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESilverman%20admits%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstatus%20of%20the%20Arabs%20(would%20be)%20affected%20to%20that%20extent%20and%20injustice%20done%20to%20them%E2%80%9D.%20Yet%20even%20if%20Arabs%20were%20to%20lose%20their%20%E2%80%9Cstatus%20in%20Palestine%20there%20would%20still%20be%20five%20independent%20kingdoms%20left%20which%20they%20(could)%20call%20their%20own%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Jews%20in%20contrast%20would%20be%20left%20with%20nothing%20if%20they%20were%20to%20lose%20Palestine.%20The%20Arabs%20could%20put%20up%20with%20a%20minor%20injustice%20in%20the%20larger%20cause%20of%20avoiding%20%E2%80%9Ca%20denial%20of%20all%20justice%20to%20the%20Jews%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGandhi%3A%20%E2%80%9CWrong%20and%20inhuman%20to%20impose%20the%20Jews%20on%20the%20Arabs%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubsequent%20events%20show%20very%20vividly%2C%20how%20this%20assertion%20of%20a%20Zionist%20right%20to%20the%20land%20was%20barely%20concealed%20cover%20for%20a%20malign%20intent.%20Zionism%20was%20always%20about%20the%20expulsion%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine%20in%20large%20numbers%2C%20destroying%20their%20centuries-long%20legacy%2C%20and%20creating%20a%20new%20state%20afresh.%20There%20was%20an%20expectation%20of%20ethnic%20purity%20in%20the%20new%20state%20which%20was%20impossible%20to%20realise%2C%20and%20with%20Palestinians%20perhaps%20in%20a%20majority%20in%20territory%20controlled%20by%20the%20Zionist%20state%20today%2C%20echoes%20of%20those%20times%20are%20now%20heard%20louder.%20Palestinians%20are%20not%20really%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%E2%80%9D%2C%20these%20voices%20proclaim%2C%20and%20their%20land%20was%20always%20a%20barren%20space%20that%20Jews%20alone%20had%20the%20mandate%20to%20occupy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20does%20not%20buy%20into%20any%20of%20these%20arguments%20even%20without%20foreknowledge%20of%20the%20malign%20shapes%20that%20Zionism%20later%20acquires.%20He%20seeks%20to%20be%20cordial%20and%20constructive%2C%20and%20suggests%20various%20options%20his%20visitors%20could%20possibly%20pursue.%20How%20Louis%20Fischer%20could%20have%20interpreted%20this%20conversation%20as%20an%20endorsement%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprior%20claim%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Jewish%20people%20is%20a%20mystery.%20Fortunately%2C%20it%20is%20one%20that%20Gandhi%20was%20quick%20to%20dispel%2C%20within%20his%20lifetime.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20prayer%20meeting%20on%20July%2014%2C%201946%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gandhiashramsevagram.org%2Fgandhi-literature%2Fmahatma-gandhi-collected-works-volume-91.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epublished%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHarijan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20July%2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E)%2C%20he%20spoke%20of%20how%20%E2%80%9Cfour%20lines%20of%20a%20newspaper%20column%E2%80%9D%20which%20a%20friend%20had%20brought%20it%20to%20his%20attention%2C%20required%20clarification.%20It%20was%20true%20that%20he%20did%20say%20%E2%80%9Csome%20such%20thing%E2%80%9D%20as%20imputed%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20course%20of%20a%20long%20conversation%20with%20Mr%20Louis%20Fischer%20on%20the%20subject%E2%80%9D.%20He%20did%20believe%20that%20the%20Jews%20had%20%E2%80%9Cbeen%20cruelly%20wronged%20by%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%20The%20term%20%E2%80%9Cghetto%E2%80%9D%20applied%20to%20Jewish%20habitations%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20Europe%2C%20eloquently%20expressed%20the%20%E2%80%9Cheartless%20persecution%E2%80%9D%20they%20had%20faced.%20That%20alone%20was%20the%20reason%20the%20%E2%80%9Creturn%20to%20Palestine%E2%80%9D%20slogan%20had%20arisen%2C%20though%20the%20world%20should%20have%20been%20the%20home%20of%20the%20Jewish%20people%2C%20if%20only%20for%20%E2%80%9Ctheir%20distinguished%20contribution%20to%20it%E2%80%9D.%20For%20all%20that%2C%20the%20Jews%20had%20%E2%80%9Cerred%20grievously%20in%20seeking%20to%20impose%20themselves%20on%20Palestine%20with%20the%20aid%20of%20America%20and%20Britain%20and%20now%20with%20the%20aid%20of%20naked%20terrorism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20take%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20conversations%20with%20Silverman%20and%20Fischer%20out%20of%20their%20context%20and%20disregard%20the%20explicit%20clarification%20he%20issued%2C%20is%20strongly%20suggestive%20of%20an%20intent%20to%20mislead.%20The%20slim%20evidence%20advanced%20by%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20does%20not%20in%20any%20case%2C%20outweigh%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20long%20trail%20of%20public%20remarks%20on%20the%20topic%2C%20beginning%20with%20his%20famous%20statement%20of%201938%2C%20that%20Palestine%20belongs%20to%20Arabs%20the%20same%20way%20that%20France%20and%20England%20belong%20to%20the%20French%20and%20the%20English.%20In%20his%20brief%201938%20essay%20titled%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gandhiashramsevagram.org%2Fgandhi-literature%2Fmahatma-gandhi-collected-works-volume-74.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Jews%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20Gandhi%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20said%20much%20more.%20It%20was%20%E2%80%9Cwrong%20and%20inhuman%20to%20impose%20the%20Jews%20on%20the%20Arabs%E2%80%9D.%20The%20colonisation%20of%20Palestine%20by%20the%20Zionists%20could%20not%20be%20%E2%80%9Cjustified%20by%20any%20moral%20code%20of%20conduct%E2%80%9D.%20And%20the%20ostensible%20%E2%80%9Cmandate%E2%80%9D%20under%20which%20it%20was%20carried%20out%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20sanction%20but%20that%20of%20the%20last%20war%E2%80%9D.%20The%20programme%20of%20reducing%20the%20Arabs%20to%20an%20alien%20presence%20in%20their%20own%20land%20was%20in%20this%20respect%2C%20little%20less%20than%20%E2%80%9Ca%20crime%20against%20humanity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20leaves%20Pyarelal%E2%80%99s%20averments%20as%20the%20sole%20basis%20on%20which%20to%20conclude%20that%20not%20enough%20is%20known%20about%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20towards%20Israel.%20Ved%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20book%20records%20this%20among%20a%20whole%20series%20of%20eccentric%20locutions.%20Pyarelal%20was%20for%20instance%2C%20ambiguous%20about%20what%20he%20would%20do%20with%20the%20large%20cache%20of%20papers%20he%20held.%20Their%20ultimate%20destination%20he%20indicated%2C%20could%20be%20the%20National%20Archives%2C%20the%20Gandhi%20Memorial%20Trust%2C%20or%20a%20trust%20to%20be%20set%20up%20in%20his%20(Pyarelal%E2%80%99s)%20memory.%20He%20was%20also%20at%20the%20time%2C%20engaged%20in%20writing%20a%20biography%20of%20Gandhi%20and%20may%20have%20retained%20papers%20beyond%20the%20time%20warranted%20in%20a%20work%20described%20by%20Mehta%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Chagiography%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResponding%20to%20an%20inquiry%2C%20Tridip%20Suhrud%2C%20an%20Ahmedabad-based%20scholar%20who%20worked%20to%20bring%20the%20Kallenbach%20papers%20back%20to%20India%2C%20told%20this%20writer%20that%20Pyarelal%20was%20not%20sole%20custodian%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20papers%2C%20and%20only%20briefly%20a%20member%20of%20the%20editorial%20board%20of%20the%20CWMG.%20Since%20his%20death%20in%201982%2C%20Pyarelal%E2%80%99s%20papers%20were%20transferred%2C%20though%20only%20after%20an%20unexplained%20gap%20of%2025%20years%2C%20to%20the%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%20in%20Delhi%20(now%20the%20Prime%20Ministers%E2%80%99%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAny%20proposition%20that%20Gandhi%20actually%20approved%20of%20the%20Zionist%20project%20can%2C%20in%20short%2C%20be%20easily%20tested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20do%20not%20have%20to%20be%20advanced%20as%20speculative%20propositions%20that%20impute%20beliefs%20and%20intentions%20not%20expressed%20during%20his%20lifetime.%20That%20these%20efforts%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Zionist%20state%20is%20embarked%20on%20its%20most%20savage%20campaign%20of%20genocide%20yet%2C%20is%20little%20else%20than%20an%20attempt%20at%20making%20Gandhi%20an%20accomplice%20in%20the%20last%20great%20crime%20of%20colonialism.%20No%20greater%20slur%20can%20be%20imagined%20to%20legacy%20of%20the%20Mahatma.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESukumar%20Muralidharan%20is%20an%20independent%20writer%20and%20researcher%20based%20in%20the%20Delhi%20region.%20He%20has%20worked%20in%20print%20media%2C%20as%20a%20journalism%20instructor%20and%20trainer%2C%20and%20press%20freedom%20campaigner.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699763443000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F02143728%2Fgandhi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fresisting-the-zionist-revisionism-of-gandhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20effort%20to%20rewrite%20the%20record%20on%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20towards%20Palestine%20and%20the%20Jewish%20question%20has%20been%20underway%20since%20long.%20Recent%20events%20in%20Gaza%20have%20given%20this%20effort%20a%20new%20impetus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fresisting-the-zionist-revisionism-of-gandhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Gorgeous%20Winter%20Flowers%20That%20Thrive%20In%20the%20Cold%3A%20How%20to%20Grow%20Them%20At%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20winters%2C%20the%20sun%20seems%20a%20little%20weaker%2C%20and%20the%20air%20carries%20that%20peculiar%20scent%20that%20tickles%20my%20nostrils%20just%20right.%20While%20this%20may%20not%20hold%20true%20for%20everyone%2C%20my%20little%20soul%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F75375%2Ftbi-blogs-five-winter-vegetables-grow-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethrives%20in%20winter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Fluffy%20coats%2C%20hot%20chocolates%2C%20and%20cosy%20blankets%20%E2%80%94%20who%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20adore%20this%20season%3F%20But%20what%20excites%20me%20the%20most%20is%20seeing%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20terrace%20garden%20adorned%20with%20a%20colourful%20blanket%20of