20our%20precious%20little%20flower%2C%20Dahlia.%20These%20flowers%20come%20in%20various%20shapes%2C%20sizes%2C%20and%20colours%2C%20from%20small%2C%20delicate%20pompons%20to%20large%2C%20showy%20dinner-plate-sized%20blossoms.%20Dahlias%20are%20not%20only%20attractive%20but%20also%20relatively%20low-maintenance%2C%20making%20them%20a%20perfect%20addition%20to%20winter%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETips%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDahlias%20can%20produce%20large%2C%20heavy%20blooms%2C%20and%20as%20they%20grow%2C%20they%20may%20need%20support%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20bending%20or%20breaking.%20Use%20stakes%20or%20cages%20to%20provide%20support%20to%20the%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20deadheading%20is%20encouraged%20with%20Dahlias%20as%20well%20to%20redirect%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20energy%20into%20blooming%20more%20new%20flowers.%20You%20can%20simply%20pinch%20or%20snip%20off%20the%20dead%20blooms%20as%20they%20wither.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fflowers-1699601137.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dahlia's%20grow%20in%20smaller%20to%20dinner-plate-size%2C%20so%20make%20sure%20you%20have%20plenty%20of%20space%20for%20them%20to%20grow.%20Deadheading%20is%20encouraged%20with%20Dahlias.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fflowers-1699601137.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fflowers-1699601137-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fflowers-1699601137-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fflowers-1699601137-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fflowers-1699601137-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333981%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDahlia%E2%80%99s%20grow%20in%20smaller%20to%20dinner-plate-size%2C%20so%20make%20sure%20you%20have%20plenty%20of%20space%20for%20them%20to%20grow.%20Deadheading%20is%20encouraged%20with%20Dahlias.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Free%20Images%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699763400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fflowers-1-1699601192.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333977%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20to%20grow%20flowers%20in%20winter%3F%20Here%20are%20some%20tips%20to%20maintain%20your%20garden%20and%20brighten%20it%20up%20with%20flowers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333977%2Fmaintaining-plants-flowers-during-winter-cold-season-in-india-gardening-tips%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20May%20Record%20Best%20Diwali%20Air%20Quality%20In%208%20Years%20If%20Cracker%20Ban%20Works%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20stringent%20enforcement%20of%20the%20ban%20on%20firecrackers%20holds%20the%20promise%20of%20delivering%20the%20best%20air%20quality%20on%20Diwali%20day%20in%20eight%20years%20for%20Delhi%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhiites%20woke%20up%20to%20clear%20skies%20and%20abundant%20sunshine%2C%20and%20the%20city's%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20stood%20at%20202%20at%207%20am%2C%20the%20best%20in%20at%20least%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AQI%20between%20zero%20and%2050%20is%20considered%20'good'%2C%2051%20and%20100%20'satisfactory'%2C%20101%20and%20200%20'moderate'%2C%20201%20and%20300%20'poor'%2C%20301%20and%20400%20'very%20poor'%2C%20401%20and%20450%20'severe'%20and%20above%20450%20'severe%20plus'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaturday's%2024-hour%20average%20air%20quality%20index%20stood%20at%20220%2C%20the%20lowest%20for%20the%20day%20before%20Diwali%20in%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20Delhi%20saw%20a%20sharp%20improvement%20in%20air%20quality%20just%20ahead%20of%20Diwali%20which%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20intermittent%20rainfall%20on%20Friday%20and%20wind%20speed%20favourable%20for%20the%20dispersion%20of%20pollutants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20this%20in%20perspective%2C%20Thursday's%2024-hour%20average%20AQI%20stood%20at%20437.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20recorded%20an%20AQI%20of%20312%20on%20Diwali%20last%20year%2C%20382%20in%202021%2C%20414%20in%202020%2C%20337%20in%202019%2C%20281%20in%202018%2C%20319%20in%202017%2C%20and%20431%20in%202016%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20experienced%20%26quot%3Bvery%20poor%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bsevere%26quot%3B%20air%20quality%20for%20two%20weeks%20starting%20October%2028%20and%20a%20suffocating%20haze%20lingered%20over%20the%20capital%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD%20had%20earlier%20predicted%20a%20marginal%20improvement%20in%20the%20air%20quality%20just%20ahead%20of%20Diwali%2C%20owing%20to%20favourable%20meteorological%20conditions%2C%20including%20light%20rain%2C%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20a%20western%20disturbance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20western%20disturbance%20led%20to%20rains%20over%20most%20parts%20of%20northwest%20India%2C%20including%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20effectively%20reducing%20the%20contribution%20of%20smoke%20from%20stubble%20burning%20to%20Delhi's%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20western%20disturbance%20passes%2C%20the%20wind%20speed%20will%20increase%20to%20around%2015%20kilometres%20per%20hour%20on%20November%2011%20(Saturday)%20which%20will%20help%20disperse%20pollutants%20ahead%20of%20Diwali%20(November%2012)%2C%20an%20IMD%20official%20said%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20accordance%20with%20the%20practice%20of%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20Delhi%20has%20announced%20a%20comprehensive%20ban%20on%20the%20manufacture%2C%20storage%2C%20sale%2C%20and%20use%20of%20firecrackers%20within%20the%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20sporadic%20incidents%20of%20firecracker%20burning%20were%20reported%20on%20Saturday%20night%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELow%20temperatures%20and%20firecracker%20burning%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20pollution%20levels%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Sunday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20decrease%20in%20stubble-burning%20incidents%2C%20delayed%20spells%20of%20rain%2C%20favourable%20meteorological%20conditions%2C%20and%20an%20early%20Diwali%20prevented%20the%20national%20capital%20from%20turning%20into%20a%20gas%20chamber%20following%20the%20festival%20of%20lights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Decision%20Support%20System%2C%20a%20numerical%20model-based%20framework%20capable%20of%20identifying%20the%20sources%20of%20particulate%20matter%20pollution%20in%20Delhi%2C%20stubble%20burning%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20states%2C%20particularly%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20accounted%20for%2023%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20city%20on%20Wednesday.%20It%20was%2033%20per%20cent%20on%20Thursday%20and%2010%20per%20cent%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20also%20shows%20that%20transport%20is%20another%20major%20factor%2C%20contributing%2012%20to%2014%20per%20cent%20to%20Delhi's%20foul%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinay%20Kumar%20Sehgal%2C%20principal%20scientist%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi-based%20Indian%20Agricultural%20Research%20Institute%2C%20anticipated%20a%20reduction%20in%20farm%20fires%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20around%20Diwali%20due%20to%20wet%20conditions%20following%20rainfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Delhi%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20said%20the%20government%20has%20postponed%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20odd-even%20car%20rationing%20scheme%20as%20there%20has%20been%20a%20notable%20improvement%20in%20the%20city's%20air%20quality%20due%20to%20the%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20government%20will%20review%20the%20air%20quality%20situation%20after%20Diwali%20and%20a%20call%20on%20the%20'odd-even'%20scheme%20may%20be%20taken%20if%20there's%20a%20sharp%20increase%20in%20pollution%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERai%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%20scheme%20would%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20city%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20reviewed%20its%20effectiveness%20and%20issued%20an%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20questioned%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20car-rationing%20scheme%2C%20aimed%20at%20curbing%20vehicular%20pollution%2C%20and%20referred%20to%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Ball%20optics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnticipating%20further%20deterioration%20of%20the%20air%20quality%20post-Diwali%2C%20Rai%20on%20Monday%20announced%20that%20the%20scheme%2C%20which%20permits%20cars%20to%20operate%20on%20alternate%20days%20based%20on%20the%20odd%20or%20even%20last%20digit%20of%20their%20registration%20numbers%2C%20would%20be%20enforced%20between%20November%2013%20and%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20say%20breathing%20in%20the%20polluted%20air%20of%20Delhi%20is%20equivalent%20to%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20smoking%20approximately%2010%20cigarettes%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProlonged%20exposure%20to%20high%20levels%20of%20pollution%20can%20cause%20or%20exacerbate%20respiratory%20problems%20such%20as%20asthma%2C%20bronchitis%20and%20chronic%20obstructive%20pulmonary%20disease%20(COPD)%20and%20dramatically%20raise%20the%20risk%20of%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStringent%20restrictions%20mandated%20under%20the%20final%20stage%20of%20the%20Centre's%20air%20pollution%20control%20plan%20for%20Delhi-NCR%20--%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20--%20have%20also%20been%20implemented%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restrictions%20under%20stage%20IV%20of%20the%20GRAP%2C%20including%20a%20ban%20on%20all%20kinds%20of%20construction%20work%20and%20the%20entry%20of%20polluting%20trucks%20into%20Delhi%2C%20took%20effect%20on%20Sunday%20after%20the%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20city%20dropped%20to%20'severe%20plus'%20(AQI%20above%20450)%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGRAP%20categorises%20actions%20into%20four%20stages%3A%20Stage%20I%20--%20Poor%20(AQI%20201-300)%3B%20Stage%20II%20--%20Very%20Poor%20(AQI%20301-400)%3B%20Stage%20III%20--%20Severe%20(AQI%20401-450)%20and%20Stage%20IV%20--%20Severe%20Plus%20(AQI%20above%20450).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfavourable%20meteorological%20conditions%2C%20combined%20with%20vehicular%20emissions%2C%20paddy-straw%20burning%2C%20firecrackers%20and%20other%20local%20pollution%20sources%2C%20contribute%20to%20hazardous%20air%20quality%20levels%20in%20the%20Delhi-NCR%20during%20winters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Delhi%20Pollution%20Control%20Committee%20(DPCC)%20analysis%2C%20the%20city%20experiences%20peak%20pollution%20from%20November%201%20to%2015%2C%20when%20the%20number%20of%20stubble-burning%20incidents%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20increases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20air%20quality%20ranks%20among%20the%20worst%20in%20the%20world's%20capital%20cities.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20compiled%20by%20the%20Energy%20Policy%20Institute%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%20(EPIC)%20in%20August%2C%20air%20pollution%20is%20shortening%20lives%20by%20almost%2012%20years%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699761240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F