hmedabad%E2%80%99s%20Kalupur%20railway%20station%20and%20is%20more%20than%20500%20years%20old%2C%20has%20been%20slapped%20with%20an%20eviction%20notice%20by%20the%20railway%20authorities%20to%20make%20way%20for%20redevelopment%20of%20the%20railway%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shrine%E2%80%99s%20management%2C%20which%20moved%20the%20Gujarat%20high%20court%2C%20says%20it%20has%20requisite%20documentation%20to%20disprove%20the%20railway%20authorities%E2%80%99%20contention%20that%20it%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunauthorised%20construction%E2%80%9D.%20The%20court%20has%20ordered%20authorities%20to%20maintain%20the%20status%20quo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20October%2026%20notice%2C%20issued%20by%20the%20Rail%20Land%20Development%20Authority%20(RLDA)%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20and%20the%20senior%20section%20engineer%20of%20the%20Western%20Railways%2C%20said%20redevelopment%20work%20of%20the%20Ahmedabad%20station%20will%20be%20undertaken%20soon%20and%20directed%20the%20dargah%20management%20to%20remove%20the%20structure%20within%2014%20days.%20The%20notice%20labels%20the%20dargah%20%E2%80%9Cunauthorised%E2%80%9D%20structure%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20is%20situated%20on%20the%20station%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F11155644%2F38e7e543-3504-4822-ac85-18d42613c92f.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22846%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F11155644%2F38e7e543-3504-4822-ac85-18d42613c92f.jpeg%20846w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F11155644%2F38e7e543-3504-4822-ac85-18d42613c92f-212x300.jpeg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F11155644%2F38e7e543-3504-4822-ac85-18d42613c92f-722x1024.jpeg%20722w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684503%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EEviction%20order%20received%20by%20the%20dargah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20from%20the%20Hazrat%20Kalu%20Shaheed%20Dargah%20that%20the%20nearby%20railway%20station%20and%20the%20nearby%20vicinity%20have%20derived%20their%20names%3A%20Kalupur%20railway%20station%20and%20the%20Kalupur%20Basti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Dargah%20predates%20Independence%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManzur%20Malek%2C%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20dargah%2C%20is%20appalled%20by%20the%20notice.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Holy%20Shrine%20of%20Hazrat%20Kalu%20Shaheed%20is%20more%20than%20500%20years%20old.%20Every%20day%2C%20at%20least%20500%20people%20come%20here%20to%20offer%20obeisance.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20the%20dargah%2C%20Muslims%20also%20offer%20namaz%20in%20the%20Masjid%20existing%20in%20the%20dargah%20premises%20and%20have%20been%20doing%20so%20for%20centuries.%20How%20does%20the%20dargah%20become%20illegal%20overnight%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Malek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalek%20and%20locals%20claim%20that%20they%20have%20been%20seeking%20various%20permissions%20from%20competent%20authorities%20for%20several%20years%2C%20including%20for%20using%20loudspeakers%20and%20power%20connection%2C%20which%20they%20say%2C%20have%20been%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20RLDA%20notice%20says%20that%20the%20Dargah%20interferes%20with%20the%20redevelopment%20of%20Kalupur%20Railway%20Station%2C%20the%20Dargah%20administration%20says%20that%20the%20station%20has%20expanded%20and%20developed%20without%20removing%20or%20altering%20the%20existing%20structure.%20The%20Ahmedabad%20Junction%20Railway%20Station%20is%20the%20biggest%20railway%20station%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiroz%20Khan%20Amin%20of%20the%20Sunni%20Awami%20Forum%2C%20an%20NGO%2C%20which%20has%20been%20raising%20the%20issues%20of%20mistreatment%20of%20Islamic%20shrines%20and%20mosques%2C%20says%20that%20Dargah%20has%20enough%20proof%20to%20substantiate%20that%20it%20is%20a%20recognised%20and%20authorised%20structure%2C%20predating%201947%20and%20should%20not%20be%20demolished%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdevelopment%E2%80%9D.%3Cstrong%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20dated%20dargah%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20response%20to%20the%20notice%2C%20the%20shrine%20management%20has%20pointed%20to%20different%20instances%2C%20with%20documentation%20from%20the%20government%2C%20which%20verified%20and%20authorised%20the%20existence%20of%20the%20Dargah.%20In%20particular%2C%20the%20management%20has%20a%20document%20from%201912%2C%20which%20validates%20the%20structure%20and%20its%20attached%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20also%20mentions%20that%20in%201965%2C%20the%20divisional%20superintendent%20of%20the%20railways%20wrote%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EMujavar%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Dargah%20informing%20that%20the%20Railway%20Board%20had%20decided%20to%20charge%20a%20license%20fee%20of%20Rs%201%20per%20annum%20for%20religious%20edifices%20standing%20on%20the%20railway%20land%20from%20the%20date%20of%20their%20inception.%20Had%20the%20Dargah%20been%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20management%20says%20the%20authorities%20would%20have%20never%20charged%20license%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%201972%2C%20in%20a%20letter%2C%20the%20divisional%20superintendent%20(works)%20informed%20the%20president%20of%20Kalu%20Shaheed%20Dargah%20that%20the%20licence%20fee%20was%20revised%20from%20Rs%201%20to%20Rs%2020%20per%20annum%20from%201965%20onwards.%20On%20July%2023%2C%202022%2C%20when%20the%20Waqf%20Act%2C%201995%2C%20came%20into%20force%2C%20the%20Dargah%20was%20registered%20as%20%E2%80%9CHazarat%20Kalu%20Shaheed%20(RA)%20Dargah%E2%80%9D%20and%20was%20given%20registration%20number%20(056-Ahmedabad)%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20State%20Waqf%20Board%2C%20according%20to%20the%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamshad%20Pathan%2C%20a%20social%20activist%20and%20advocate%2C%20alleges%20that%20actual%20stakeholders%20who%20would%20%E2%80%9Csuffer%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20station%20%E2%80%9Credevelopment%E2%80%9D%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Csidelined%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20decision-making%20process.%20%E2%80%9CPolicies%20should%20be%20formulated%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people%20who%20would%20actually%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pathan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDargah%2C%20devotion%20and%20demolition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContesting%20the%20notice%2C%20the%20management%20moved%20the%20Gujarat%20high%20court%2C%20which%20heard%20the%20matter%20on%20November%2010.%20Justice%20Vaibhavi%20Nanavati%20ordered%20the%20parties%20to%20maintain%20the%20status%20quo.%20The%20matter%20will%20be%20next%20heard%20on%20January%2016%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20Baldev%20Singh%20(56)%2C%20who%20has%20been%20visiting%20the%20Dargah%20for%2035%20years%2C%20says%20that%20the%20dargah%20is%20close%20to%20his%20heart%2C%20as%20it%20is%20a%20peaceful%20and%20religious%20place.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20holds%20over%20800%20years%20of%20faith%20and%20history.%20It%20has%20existed%20even%20before%20railways%20existed.%20The%20Dargah%20should%20not%20be%20touched.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20Thursday%2C%20Singh%20travels%2010%20km%20to%20visit%20the%20Dargah%2C%20a%20symbol%20of%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20syncretism.%20For%20him%20and%20many%20like%20him%2C%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Dargah%20would%20be%20a%20personal%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699695456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2FGujarat-HCX.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fgujarat-hc-puts-on-hold-eviction-order-served-on-ahmedabads-historic-dargah%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Hazrat%20Kalu%20Shaheed%2