%20was%20at%20it).%20Is%20the%20car%20unloading%20another%20party%20of%20armed%20hooligans%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers%20barricade%20themselves%20in%20their%20homes.%20Moments%20later%20they%20see%20a%20bright%20light%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Ewadi%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20settlers%20coming%20at%20us%20again%3F%20The%20light%20eventually%20retreats%3B%20they%20relax%20a%20little%2C%20if%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20right%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Azzam%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20are%20here%20and%20they%20attack%2C%20your%20presence%20might%20hold%20them%20back%20a%20bit.%E2%80%9D%20He%20speaks%20softly%2C%20as%20always%2C%20but%20I%20hear%20the%20trauma%20in%20every%20syllable.%20His%20house%20was%20badly%20hit.%20He%20was%20born%20in%20Susiya%2C%20grew%20up%20here%2C%20has%20never%20lived%20anywhere%20else.%20I%20suppose%20he%20must%20be%20in%20his%20sixties.%20But%20the%20whole%20community%20lives%20the%20danger%3B%20the%20children%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20the%20past%20but%20worse%2C%20much%20worse%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20feel%20the%20horrible%20insult%20and%20humiliation%2C%20the%20injustice%2C%20the%20helplessness%20and%20unrelenting%20fear%2C%20the%20deliberate%20laceration%20of%20manliness%20and%2C%20above%20all%2C%20of%20humanity%20itself%2C%20in%20which%20they%20allegedly%20have%20no%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09204125%2FShulman-10-1024x461.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09204125%2FShulman-10-1024x461.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09204125%2FShulman-10-300x135.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp