%22The%20banyans%20form%20an%20ecological%20corridor%20connecting%20different%20parts%20of%20Telangana%20state%20for%20many%20birds%20and%20other%20species.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333929%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20banyans%20form%20an%20ecological%20corridor%20connecting%20different%20parts%20of%20Telangana%20state%20for%20many%20birds%20and%20other%20species.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Do%20not%20doubt%20yourself%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CNone%20of%20us%20are%20lawyers%2C%20professionals%2C%20or%20in%20power.%20But%20we%20put%20in%20our%20time%20to%20read%20and%20speak%20to%20experts%20to%20understand%20the%20cause.%20It%20was%20not%20impossible.%20If%20we%20could%20do%20it%2C%20others%20can%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20four%20years%20back%2C%20somebody%20asked%20me%20to%20head%20a%20petition%20like%20this%2C%20I%20would%20have%20ended%20up%20laughing%20and%20questioning%20my%20abilities.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20could%20not%20differentiate%20between%20the%20varieties%20of%20trees.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20learning%20process%20for%20me%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20It%20is%20not%20good%20vs%20evil%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NHAI%20is%20doing%20its%20job.%20So%2C%20ideally%2C%20there%20are%20no%20real%20villains.%20However%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20highlight%20what%20constitutes%20a%20public%20benefit%20and%20a%20better%20society%2C%20and%20how%20development%20projects%20should%20learn%20to%20incorporate%20nature%20and%20rethink%20these%20definitions%20in%20the%20context%20of%20climate%20change%20and%20better%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Understand%20what%20is%20legally%20possible%20and%20legally%20viable%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETejah%20points%20out%20that%20as%20citizens%2C%20we%20may%20think%20that%20the%20national%20tree%20of%20India%20will%20have%20some%20legal%20protection%20but%20apparently%20they%20don%E2%80%99t.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20then%20have%20to%20negotiate%20a%20space%20for%20them%20in%20our%20legal%20framework.%20What%20we%20think%20is%20legal%20and%20what%20is%20viable%20become%20two%20different%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5)%20Do%20not%20get%20overwhelmed%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20nature%20is%20to%20produce%20volumes%20of%20documentation.%20Our%20job%20is%20to%20try%20to%20understand%20what%20these%20documents%20are%20and%20seek%20experts%E2%80%99%20help%20whenever%20required.%20Have%20patience%20in%20understanding%20documents%20and%20Excel%20sheets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ENature%20Lovers%20of%20Hyderabad%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699539603000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333910%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Hyderabad%2C%20citizens%20came%20together%20to%20save%20old%20banyan%20trees%20from%20being%20cut%20down%20for%20a%20new%20national%20highway.%20The%20recent%20decision%20by%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20is%20a%20big%20win%20for%20everyone.%20Here%20are%20their%20tips%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20protect%20