0Nasscom%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Devanshi%20(18)%20from%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Sirohi%20lost%20her%20father%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20needless%20to%20say%2C%20it%20left%20a%20void%20behind.%20Her%20mother%2C%20now%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333328%2Fujjain-beautician-monisha-chhabra-broke-makeup-taboos-empowered-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esole%20breadwinner%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20to%20a%20business%20of%20sewing.%20However%2C%20the%20revenue%20was%20meagre.%20With%20no%20way%20forward%20in%20sight%2C%20uncertainty%20about%20the%20future%20was%20rife.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20year%202021%2C%20hope%20was%20rekindled%20among%20the%20villagers%20in%20the%20form%20of%20digital%20resource%20centres.%20An%20endeavour%20by%20Nasscom%20Foundation%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20working%20with%20the%20tech%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20and%20IT%20pioneer%20DXC%20Technology%2C%20the%20initiative%20has%20since%20grown%20in%20scale.%20The%20partnership%20was%20conceived%20two%20years%20ago%20and%20was%20the%20coming%20together%20of%20two%20organisations%20for%20the%20greater%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDevanshi%20was%20introduced%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20world%20where%20technology%20meets%20ingenuity.%20She%20spent%20hours%20at%20the%20resource%20centre%20grasping%20the%20nuances%20of%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram.%20In%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20not%20only%20she%2C%20but%20her%20entrepreneur%20mother%20too%20were%20pros.%20Together%2C%20the%20duo%20chiselled%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325319%2Fjai-bharathi-gives-free-driving-lessons-for-women-mowo-hyderabad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20side%20to%20the%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20would%20boast%20marketing%20through%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3